Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.55,0:00:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs80\pos(960,540)\an5}SHAOHAI 影视资料档案室珍藏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:54.92,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,时至今日 我依然会问自己\N{\fs38}I still ask myself if I did the right thing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:57.72,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,当初应该离开那座海上城吗\N{\fs38}when I abandoned his floating city.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.93,0:01:02.02,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,不只是辞了工作\N{\fs38}And I don't mean only for the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:06.29,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,重要的是 那样的朋友\N{\fs38}The fact is, a friend like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.27,0:01:09.39,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,挚友\N{\fs38}a real friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.20,0:01:12.52,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,此生再难遇见\N{\fs38}you won't meet one again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.12,0:01:16.10,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,如果你决定收起水手腿\N{\fs38}If you just decide to hang up your sea legs,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.29,0:01:21.62,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,如果你想脚踏实地\N{\fs38}if you just want to feel something more solid beneath your feet,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.11,0:01:29.89,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,如果你再也听不见那天籁般的音乐\N{\fs38}and if then you no longer hear the music of the gods around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.74,0:01:36.88,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但 就像他常说的:\N{\fs38}But, like he used to say:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:42.65,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"只要你有个好故事 和听故事的人...\N{\fs38}"You're never really done for as long as you got a good story...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.36,0:01:46.44,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这就不是你的末日"\N{\fs38}and someone to tell it to."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.19,0:01:52.03,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,可问题是...\N{\fs38}Trouble is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.13,0:01:58.06,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,压根没人相信我的故事\N{\fs38}nobody'd believe a single word of my story.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:42.95,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,每次都一样...\N{\fs38}It happened everytime...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.28,0:02:49.33,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,总有人会抬起头看到她\N{\fs38}Someone would look up and see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:54.06,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,真是令人费解\N{\fs38}It's difficult to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.09,0:02:55.17,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,是这样...\N{\fs38}What I'm saying is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.26,0:03:00.74,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那艘船上少说也有一千人\N{\fs38}there were more than a thousand of us on that ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:04.37,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,旅行的富人 移民\N{\fs38}travelling richfolk, immigrants,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:07.55,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,一些怪人 还有我们\N{\fs38}and strange people, and us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:10.72,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但是 总有那么一个人!\N{\fs38}Yet, there was always one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:16.40,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就那么一个 最先看到她\N{\fs38}One guy alone who would see her first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.72,0:03:19.08,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,也许他只是坐在那里吃东西\N{\fs38}Maybe he was just sitting there eating,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.18,0:03:21.19,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,也许只是在甲板上散步\N{\fs38}or walking on the deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.58,0:03:24.31,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,也许是在缝裤子\N{\fs38}Maybe he was just fixing his pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.36,0:03:29.41,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他就那么一抬头 瞄了一眼大海\N{\fs38}He'd look up for a second, a quick glance out to sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:31.52,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就看到了她\N{\fs38}and he'd see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.45,0:03:37.99,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,傻站在原地 心跳加速\N{\fs38}Then he'd just stand there, rooted to the spot, his heart racing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:43.05,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,每一次 每一次\N{\fs38}And every time, every damn time, I swear,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:50.66,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那人都会转向我们 转向船上的人 所有人 大喊...\N{\fs38}he'd turn to us, towards the ship towards everybody and scream...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:52.83,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,美国!\N{\fs38}America!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:15.86,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,赌谁先看到她 我输了一次又一次\N{\fs38}And I lost big money betting on who'd be the first guy to see her,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:18.18,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,美国!\N{\fs38}America!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:25.44,Default-微软雅黑 粗,,0,0,0,,海上钢琴师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.47,0:05:57.12,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,真是奇迹啊 老天!\N{\fs38}It's a miracle, Santa Rosalia!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:06:01.89,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,什么老天 是圣母啊!\N{\fs38}What do you mean Santa Rosalia, it's the Madonna di Lourdes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.05,0:06:36.54,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,纽约\N{\fs38}New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:47.61,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,最先看到美国的人\N{\fs38}The one who sees America first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:50.23,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,每艘船上都有那么一个!\N{\fs38}There's one on every ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:56.15,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,别以为这是意外 也不是错觉\N{\fs38}And don't be thinking it's anaccident or some optical illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:58.97,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这是命\N{\fs38}It's destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:06.34,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那一瞬间是从生下来就被决定的\N{\fs38}Those are people who always have that precise instant stamped on their life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.35,0:07:10.69,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,当他们还小的时候 你看着他们的眼睛\N{\fs38}And when they were kids, you could look into their eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.79,0:07:16.96,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,朦胧中就有一个她\N{\fs38}and if you looked carefully enough you'd already see her,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.48,0:07:20.30,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,美国\N{\fs38}America.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.37,0:07:35.23,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我也见过几次美国!\N{\fs38}And I've seen a few Americas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:39.61,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,六年了 每年五个来回:\N{\fs38}Six years on that ship, five crossings a year:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.71,0:07:46.10,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,漂泊在美国欧洲之间 大洋之上\N{\fs38}Europe, America and back. Always soaking in the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:50.46,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,踏上陆地后 撒尿都对不准尿壶\N{\fs38}When you stepped on land you couldn't even piss straight in the john.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:53.83,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,它并不晃 我说的是尿壶\N{\fs38}It was steady. The john, I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:57.60,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,是你一直傻傻在晃\N{\fs38}but you'd keep bobbing like an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.47,0:08:02.75,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,下船容易 但放弃大海...\N{\fs38}You can get off a ship all right, but off the ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:06.64,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,正要打烊 您有事吗?\N{\fs38}I was just closing. What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.44,0:08:11.62,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,第一次上船 我还是二十四岁\N{\fs38}When I boarded I was twenty-four years old,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:15.70,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那时我只在乎一件事\N{\fs38}and I only cared about one thing in life
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.95,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,吹小号\N{\fs38}playing the trumpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.49,0:08:26.05,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我要卖这个\N{\fs38}I'm selling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:32.44,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,康牌的\N{\fs38}A Conn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:34.70,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,不错\N{\fs38}Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:42.61,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,顶级的黄铜!\N{\fs38}Best brass money can buy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:47.19,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,当年是顶级的\N{\fs38}Could buy, in its day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.54,0:08:55.35,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,很久没吹了吧?\N{\fs38}Been a while since you played, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:09:00.08,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,确实很久没有为钱演奏了\N{\fs38}If you mean for money, a couple of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:05.83,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但我的音乐 我的心血 一直没有断过\N{\fs38}But I've spit my guts through that thing to get rid of the blues console's playing and I've never stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:07.29,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,别误会...\N{\fs38}Don't get me wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.29,0:09:10.50,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,最伟大的爵士乐手也是用这个的\N{\fs38}The greatest jazz players in the world blew through brass like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:11.55,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,您说得对\N{\fs38}I'm sure, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:14.80,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但战争结束后 人们都想听明快的曲子\N{\fs38}But after the war, people want brightness thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:18.23,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,欢乐的小调 爵士都抛到一边了!\N{\fs38}sweet sounds, never mind jazz!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:21.85,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你的康牌小号 现在只能是收藏了\N{\fs38}Your conn, just a collector's item, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:28.83,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,六磅十先令 最多了\N{\fs38}Six pounds, ten shillings. Best I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:34.49,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,天啊 那也才二十五刀!\N{\fs38}Christ, that's only 25 dollars!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:38.76,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,它是我生命的一部分 师傅\N{\fs38}That horn's my whole life, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:43.23,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,虽然没人会记得我 我不是巴迪波顿 也不是"书包嘴大叔"\N{\fs38}Okay, no-body's going to remember me, like Buddy Bolden or Satchmo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.59,0:09:43.23,Default-微软雅黑 粗,,0,0,0,,{\an8} (著名的爵士演奏家)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:45.65,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那就算是无名小卒\N{\fs38}But even just being a nobody
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:48.91,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,也比二十块钱更值吧!\N{\fs38}it's got to be worth more than twenty lousy bucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:09:59.80,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,如果是按你说的 那估计这值半个皇冠了\N{\fs38}If that's how things are, I suppose it's barely worth half a crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:03.74,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,出去记得关门 谢谢\N{\fs38}Shut the door when you leave, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:12.11,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,好吧 老爷子你赢了!\N{\fs38}Okay, Pops, you win!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:18.77,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,恭喜你买下了一段音乐历史\N{\fs38}You just bought yourself a piece of musical history.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:27.14,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我建议你啊...\N{\fs38}Now, if you want my advice...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.83,0:10:33.94,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,出门逛逛 晚上吃点好的\N{\fs38}Go out, treat yourself to a decent meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.79,0:10:58.27,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,至少让我吹最后一次吧\N{\fs38}At least let me play it one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.55,0:11:01.43,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,小伙子我没时间跟你折腾!\N{\fs38}Young man I don't have time to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:06.49,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs38}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:11.76,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,快点 我马上打烊了\N{\fs38}Hurry up, then, I'm closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:13.85,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs38}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.42,0:12:59.62,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,一模一样 对不对?\N{\fs38}Two peas in a pod, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:06.44,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你还好吗? 你不会要晕在这里吧?\N{\fs38}You are all right? You aren't going to be ill here, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.48,0:13:14.72,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,是你刚刚吹的曲子 你肯定知道?\N{\fs38}It's the music you were just playing. Sure you recognise it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:15.88,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这是什么曲\N{\fs38}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:23.89,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,它没有名字\N{\fs38}It doesn't have a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:30.32,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,只有很少的人才有幸听过它\N{\fs38}Just a handful of people have had the privilege of hearing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:41.22,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这曲风\N{\fs38}That style.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:44.06,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我今早就一直在想...\N{\fs38}I was wondering since this morning, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.16,0:13:49.42,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,想不出这位杰出的钢琴家是谁\N{\fs38}I can't work out who this amazing piano player is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:53.81,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你应该没听过他的名字\N{\fs38}I don't think you've ever heard of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:55.31,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,是谁?\N{\fs38}Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.47,0:14:02.30,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,如果我说他从没存在过 那也绝非虚言\N{\fs38}If I told you that this pianist never existed, I wouldn't be lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:07.29,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢遮遮掩掩的 会藏污垢 臭死了!\N{\fs38}I don't like secrets. They stink, like dirty underwear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.29,0:14:11.42,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,快点告诉我 到底是谁弹的?\N{\fs38}Come on now, Yank, who the devil is playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:23.24,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这是我的秘密\N{\fs38}It's my secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.80,0:15:03.04,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那是本世纪开头第一年\N{\fs38}It was the first year of this frigging century,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.20,0:15:06.94,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,维吉尼亚号上一个看不出肤色的挖煤工说的\N{\fs38}as timed by an unknowncolored coal stoker on the Virginian.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:11.59,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这些富得流油的混蛋!\N{\fs38}Fucking rich-ass bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.61,0:15:15.84,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,除了烟屁股和脏手帕 什么都不会忘带!\N{\fs38}Can't lose nothing but cigarette butts and dirty-ass handkerchiefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:20.50,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就不能落一只手表\N{\fs38}Can't lose no watch,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:24.30,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,哪怕是一块坏的埃尔金表 或者丑爆的袖扣啊\N{\fs38}not even a beat-up Elginor a sorry-ass cufflink.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:28.49,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,想什么呢? 连假戒指都找不到!\N{\fs38}What am I talking about? Not even a fake fucking ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:32.98,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,看 一根完整的雪茄!\N{\fs38}Hey, look here, a whole cigar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.44,0:15:36.24,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,看来这聚会上还是有穷人的\N{\fs38}Must've been somebody poor at the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.71,0:15:41.73,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这地板脏的! 恶心死了!\N{\fs38}Look at this shit! Nasty fucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.39,0:15:47.66,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,有钱人真行 不欠你钱就一毛不拔\N{\fs38}Damn rich. Don't forget nothing unless they owe you some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:56.37,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你怎么在这?\N{\fs38}What in the scuts you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:05.26,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,T·D·莱蒙\N{\fs38}T.D. Lemons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.45,0:16:17.16,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你好哇 莱蒙!\N{\fs38}Howdy do there, Lemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:19.83,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那些移民鬼!\N{\fs38}Immigrant bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.49,0:16:23.87,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,躲在甲板暗处偷偷生了\N{\fs38}Give birth in secret somewhere on deck,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.97,0:16:27.06,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我们船上就多一个负担\N{\fs38}and then leave on the ship another mouth to feed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:30.94,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这移民局可要找上门来了!\N{\fs38}And that's a big trouble with the immigration office!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:33.61,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这种小屁孩长大之后会变成怎样?\N{\fs38}What's a boy like him going to be when the baby grows up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.71,0:16:35.62,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,继续当移民呗!\N{\fs38}Another immigrant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:39.06,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,别管那些混蛋 莱蒙\N{\fs38}Don't pay those bastards no mind, Lemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.07,0:16:41.03,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,来吧 喝吧 乖宝宝!\N{\fs38}Go on, lap it up boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:45.68,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,虽然不是你妈的乳汁 但这可是真的牛奶\N{\fs38}It's not you mama's tip, but it's real milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:47.08,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,喝吧!\N{\fs38}Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:53.13,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就这小鬼 他们把它留在一等舱的钢琴上\N{\fs38}This one they left in first class on top the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.23,0:16:56.11,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,希望有富人能带走他\N{\fs38}They are hoping some rich guy will come take it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:57.82,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,让他幸福\N{\fs38}and give him a happy life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:17:00.71,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,- 不是吗 丹尼? - 你怎么想的?\N{\fs38}- Isn't that so, Danny? - What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.90,0:17:07.44,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,看这小鬼最后落到谁手上了? 一个穷得要死的黑鬼!\N{\fs38}And who does the little ape get instead? A poor worthless nigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:19.35,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,去你的 说我穷 你个臭老鼠!\N{\fs38}Fuck poverty, you stinking sewer rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:29.33,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,TD两个字写在盒子上面 你们这些蠢货知道那是什么意思吗?\N{\fs38}T.D. was written on the box. Any of you shitheads know what that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:32.28,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我忘了 你们都不识字!\N{\fs38}I forgot, You all can't read!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.33,0:17:33.74,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我告诉你们吧\N{\fs38}I'll tell you what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:36.53,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,意思就是"谢谢丹尼" "谢谢丹尼"\N{\fs38}It means, "Thanks, Danny.""Thanks, Danny"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.63,0:17:38.83,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他们是给我留的 我要养大他\N{\fs38}They left that boy for me and I'm keeping him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:40.71,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你们就滚一边吧\N{\fs38}Rest of you all can go fuck yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.71,0:17:44.41,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,丹尼 你给那小鬼头取个什么名?\N{\fs38}Danny, what are you going to call the nino?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:48.15,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我还没想过\N{\fs38}Hell, I didn't think about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:54.26,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,首先 就以我命名吧 丹尼·博德曼\N{\fs38}To start off, I name him after me, Danny Boodman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:59.83,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,然后把T·D放中间 就跟那些富人写在袖口上的缩写一样\N{\fs38}Then I'll put T.D. in the middle like the rich folks puts on their cuff-links in shirts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.42,0:18:03.25,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,有个中间名一下就上档次了 不觉得吗?\N{\fs38}That give it class, to put that in the middle, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.34,0:18:07.40,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,所有律师名字中间都有个缩写\N{\fs38}All fucking lawyers gots initials in the middle of their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:10.64,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我一个律师就叫乔纳森·P·T·K·旺德\N{\fs38}One of mine own was Jonathan P.T.K. Wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:13.18,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,是那个送你进监狱呆了十年的律师吗?\N{\fs38}The one who sent you straight to jail for ten years?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.18,0:18:16.12,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你记性倒是不赖啊 中国佬!\N{\fs38}You got one good memory, chicky China man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:20.37,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,如果我儿子长大变成律师 我就亲手杀了他!\N{\fs38}If my son grow up to be a lawyer, I swear i'll kill him myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.44,0:18:25.19,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但这孩子的名字还是丹尼·博德曼·T·D·莱蒙\N{\fs38}But the boy's name is still going to be Danny Boodman T.D. Lemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.32,0:18:27.40,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你们觉得呢?\N{\fs38}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.40,0:18:29.85,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你喜欢就好 丹尼 你是他妈!\N{\fs38}You got to like it, Danny. You're the mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.53,0:18:35.45,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这名字很稳妥 但是太短了 也没有韵味\N{\fs38}I like it firmly, but it's short.I mean, it got no finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.52,0:18:38.10,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,又不是什么皇亲贵族的子孙 丹尼!\N{\fs38}He ain't the son of no fucking duke, Danny!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.10,0:18:41.50,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,周二找到的 就叫周二吧!\N{\fs38}You found him on a Tuesday, call him Tuesday!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.30,0:18:46.84,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你没你看起来那么蠢 老黑!\N{\fs38}You ain't as dumb as you look, colored boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:52.37,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,既然是新世纪第一年第一个月找到他的\N{\fs38}I found him the first month ofthe first year of this frigging new century,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:56.24,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那么我就叫他1900!\N{\fs38}So I'm calling him Nineteen Hundred!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.23,0:19:00.22,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,1900? 那是个数字啊!\N{\fs38}Nineteen Hundred? But that's a number!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:01.85,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,原来是个数 现在是个名字了!\N{\fs38}It was a number, now it's a name!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:07.67,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,丹尼·博德曼·T·D·莱蒙·1900!\N{\fs38}Danny Boodman T.D. Lemon Nineteen Hundred!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:13.37,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,丹尼 你的小屁孩不高兴了!\N{\fs38}Danny, your little bambino is not so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.37,0:19:17.89,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,来了 快 快 别担心 你妈在这呢\N{\fs38}Come on, hurry, Hurry up. Don't worry, your mama's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:26.35,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,该死 你这么小 怎么拉那么多?\N{\fs38}Damn. How can something that small shit so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:38.76,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,# 齿轮在转 #\N{\fs38}# the wheels are turning #
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:41.72,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,# 蒸汽在喷 #\N{\fs38}# the Steam keeps on rising #
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.92,0:19:47.08,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,# 上帝 请给予我们光与亮 #\N{\fs38}# oh Lord send down your light today #
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:48.78,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,谢谢丹尼?\N{\fs38}Thanks Danny?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:51.93,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,谢谢丹尼?\N{\fs38}Thanks Danny?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.53,0:19:55.94,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,# 孩子在哭 #\N{\fs38}# A child is crying #
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.04,0:19:59.47,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,# 生命伊始 #\N{\fs38}# a new life is starting #
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.57,0:20:04.14,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,# 上帝 请与我们底层人同在 #\N{\fs38}# oh Lord stay with us here below #
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.24,0:20:06.30,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,谢谢丹尼\N{\fs38}Thanks Danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.71,0:20:10.08,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,谢谢丹尼\N{\fs38}Thanks Danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.18,0:20:16.40,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,# 有一天孩子会长大成熟 #\N{\fs38}# One day this boy will tell a tale or two #
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:21.80,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,# 现在他的灵魂在你手中 #\N{\fs38}# for now his soul is in your hand #
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:26.90,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,谢谢丹尼...\N{\fs38}Thanks Danny...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:30.18,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就像是耶稣又诞生了\N{\fs38}It was like the second coming of Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:35.29,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,也许是因为那小鬼手臂上的肌肉\N{\fs38}Maybe it was that, with all the miracles that little kid had up his sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:38.92,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,除了走之外 没什么是他不能在水上做的\N{\fs38}Hell, he did everything on the water but walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:42.21,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,听说他也能水上漂\N{\fs38}And I heard he'd done that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:50.47,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,1900就是这么成长的\N{\fs38}And that's how little Nineteen Hundred grew up
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.58,0:20:53.63,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,船就是他的摇篮\N{\fs38}Inside that cradle as big as a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.83,0:20:56.71,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但由于丹尼怕有人会因为\N{\fs38}But, since Danny was afraid they'd take him away
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:21:00.34,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,文件和签证什么的把他带走\N{\fs38}on account of some business concerning documents and visas,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:04.13,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这孩子小的时候一直躲在\N{\fs38}the boy lived his early years always hiding
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:06.68,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,维吉尼亚号的船肚里\N{\fs38}in the belly of the Virginian.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:41.65,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,好 你自己试一个\N{\fs38}Okay, now try one for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:44.24,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,来 看这里 手指指着字\N{\fs38}Now, look here. Push your finger against these words,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:47.12,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这样它们就不会跑掉了!\N{\fs38}So the letters can't run off on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:48.80,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"芒"\N{\fs38}"Man"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:50.31,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,好 继续\N{\fs38}All right, keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.09,0:21:52.76,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"果"\N{\fs38}"Go"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.33,0:21:54.40,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,继续\N{\fs38}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.40,0:21:55.60,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,妈\N{\fs38}"Ma"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.60,0:21:56.82,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,还有一点点\N{\fs38}Just a little bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.92,0:21:58.23,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"妈"\N{\fs38}"Ma"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.86,0:22:02.24,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你太会读了 莱蒙!\N{\fs38}Boy, you read like a god, Lemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.30,0:22:05.83,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,来 连起来读 像水龙头一样哗哗流\N{\fs38}Now, go on, put them all together, kind of like them boiler valves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.58,0:22:08.86,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,加油\N{\fs38}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:15.89,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"芒果妈妈"\N{\fs38}"Man... Go... Mama"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.25,0:22:20.79,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,芒果妈妈 好的 继续\N{\fs38}Mango Mama. All right. Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.06,0:22:26.81,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"拽链子"\N{\fs38}"Ya-nk my ch-ain"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.73,0:22:31.68,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,丹尼 你怎么笑成这样?\N{\fs38}Danny, why are you laughing so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.68,0:22:34.55,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,因为这些都是马的名字啊 你不觉得好笑吗?\N{\fs38}Because these are names of horses. Don't that make you laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.55,0:22:37.14,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我太爱这些马的名字了 你看这个\N{\fs38}I'm just crazy about these horses' names. Look at this one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.14,0:22:38.99,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就这儿 那匹昨天在克里夫兰比赛的\N{\fs38}Read there, that one ran yesterday at Cleveland.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.20,0:22:41.87,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"欢乐舞者"\N{\fs38}"Ha-ppy Hoo-fers".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.58,0:22:47.09,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,听这个\N{\fs38}Listen to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.30,0:22:49.07,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"时髦少女"\N{\fs38}"Sa-ssy La-ssy".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.17,0:22:50.98,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,时髦少女!\N{\fs38}Sassy Lassy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.21,0:22:55.60,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,还有这个 "火辣妈妈"\N{\fs38}And this one, "Red Hot Mama"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.62,0:23:03.10,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,什么是妈妈 丹尼?\N{\fs38}What's a mama, Danny?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.08,0:23:05.44,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,妈妈?\N{\fs38}A mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.68,0:23:09.46,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,妈妈就是一匹马!\N{\fs38}A mama's a horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.46,0:23:10.77,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,马?\N{\fs38}A horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.77,0:23:11.97,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,赛马\N{\fs38}Racehorse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.07,0:23:15.80,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,其实吧 妈妈是世界上最好的马\N{\fs38}Matter of fact, you know what I say. Mama's the best horse in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.80,0:23:18.67,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,血统纯 赌注下在妈妈身上 不会输的\N{\fs38}Thoroughbred, You bet on a mama, you always win.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.44,0:23:32.16,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"塔诺·达马多 柠檬之王"\N{\fs38}"Tano d'amato the King of Lemons"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.19,0:23:35.28,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,爸 你手指拿过来 你看\N{\fs38}Dad, put your finger here and read.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.38,0:23:39.57,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,T.D.不是"谢谢丹尼"的意思\N{\fs38}T.D. doesn't mean "Thanks, Danny"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.58,0:23:43.62,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这是什么鬼东西?\N{\fs38}Who's this pansy ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.89,0:23:48.38,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,今天就读到这里吧 书读得太多对你不好!\N{\fs38}That's enough reading for tonight. Too much reading's bad for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.38,0:23:53.15,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,还有什么不好 丹尼?\N{\fs38}What else is bad, Danny?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.52,0:23:56.30,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,维吉尼亚号以外的都是不好的\N{\fs38}Everything off the Virginian is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.59,0:23:59.60,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,都不好\N{\fs38}Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.30,0:24:02.77,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,陆地上有鲨鱼 直接把你活吞了\N{\fs38}They got sharks on the land, they eat you alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.77,0:24:05.00,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你好好呆着别被咬 听到没?\N{\fs38}You keep away from they, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.95,0:24:08.79,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,看这块\N{\fs38}See this here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.96,0:24:11.40,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这是大白鲨咬的 最可怕的那种\N{\fs38}That's the white sharks, worst kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.50,0:24:14.18,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,丹尼 孤儿院是什么?\N{\fs38}Danny, what's an orphanage?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.21,0:24:19.54,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,孤儿院是一个大监狱\N{\fs38}Well, a orphanage is like a great big prison
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.54,0:24:21.56,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,专门关没有孩子的人的\N{\fs38}where they lock up folks that ain't got kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.56,0:24:26.64,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那所以如果我没在你身边 他们就把你送去孤儿院?\N{\fs38}So if I wasn't with you they would put you in an orphanage?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.18,0:24:32.94,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你说对了 小莱蒙 晚安\N{\fs38}You got that right, little Lemon. Night-night.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.11,0:24:39.16,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,在那艘名叫维吉尼亚号的海上城里 除了他爸\N{\fs38}On that extraordinary floating city called Virginian, more than a father,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.46,0:24:45.29,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,1900还有一帮稀奇古怪的家人\N{\fs38}Nineteen Hundred found a whole family made of truly unique people,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.39,0:24:46.57,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,比如船上的医生\N{\fs38}like the ship's doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.57,0:24:48.96,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,张嘴 就这样\N{\fs38}Open your mouth, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.78,0:24:57.80,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,天啊 医生 你喉咙怎么有个红东西挂在那里? 你生病了吗?\N{\fs38}Shit, doctor, what's that red thing hanging from your throat? Are you sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.85,0:25:01.27,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你叫什么 医生?\N{\fs38}What's your name, doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.76,0:25:06.14,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我是克劳斯曼皮兹维根多芬塔基医生\N{\fs38}Dr Klausermanspizwegensdorfentage.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.30,0:25:10.19,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,真够长的! 如果有谁要着急喊你 那可得好大一口气!\N{\fs38}What a name! If they had to call you quickly , they've had garner!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.11,0:25:12.66,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,圈子里所有人...\N{\fs38}All that circus...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.68,0:25:16.92,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,厨师 水手 无线员 服务生们\N{\fs38}cooks, sailors, radio operators and waiters
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.02,0:25:19.07,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,把他照料的好好的\N{\fs38}took good care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.40,0:25:26.42,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,都在用自己的方式 给他自认为最好的教育\N{\fs38}And in their own way tried to give him what they thought was a good education.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.48,0:25:35.53,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,船长也一样 用自己独特的方式管教他\N{\fs38}Also the ship's Captain, other than that, he ended up being part of that crazy family.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.02,0:25:40.15,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,史密斯船长是一位智者 只有三个弱点:\N{\fs38}Captain Smith, a wise man, he only had three defects:
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.51,0:25:44.64,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他有幽闭恐惧症 害怕淹死\N{\fs38}He suffered from claustrophobia, had a horrible fear of drowning,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.81,0:25:47.36,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,厌恶甜食\N{\fs38}and he hated sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.64,0:25:53.55,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,1900 我跟你说了多少次了 不要上这儿来\N{\fs38}Nineteen Hundred, how many times have I told you not to come up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.55,0:25:56.01,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,尤其是别来偷东西!\N{\fs38}Especially if it's to steal!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.08,0:26:00.53,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,给我乖乖放回去 回自己屋里呆着\N{\fs38}Put the booty back where you found it and return to your den
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.53,0:26:02.19,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,要不我就把你送去孤儿院!\N{\fs38}or i'll send you to the orphanage!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.19,0:26:03.17,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,快!\N{\fs38}Quick...!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.70,0:26:11.44,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,丹尼·博德曼先生 这个捣蛋孤儿必须管管了!\N{\fs38}Mr. Danny Boodman, this orphan nuts must come to an end!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.61,0:26:15.28,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,说起来 这根本就是违法的\N{\fs38}On the case, it's even against the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.55,0:26:18.17,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,去他的法律!\N{\fs38}Fuck the law!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.17,0:26:59.26,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,嘿 米克 你觉得在风暴中间怎么样呀?\N{\fs38}Hey, Mick, what do you think about in the middle of a storm?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.38,0:27:04.93,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,什么? 我觉得那律师从娘胎出来就是浪费?\N{\fs38}What? Do I think my lawyer should never have been born?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.06,0:27:08.14,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,没错 就这风暴\N{\fs38}Yes, the storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.61,0:27:13.16,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那肯定下手打爆他脑袋前打过招呼啦!\N{\fs38}You bet he was warned, then I blew off his head!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.69,0:27:16.15,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你在想果酱面包?\N{\fs38}You think of jam and bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.43,0:27:17.64,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fs38}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.33,0:27:22.33,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我怎么说你呢 米克? 你脑子就是秀逗了!\N{\fs38}Know what I think, Mick? I think you're loco!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.37,0:27:24.36,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我的爱好?\N{\fs38}I have gusto?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.08,0:27:31.64,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,丹尼 跟佩德罗讲讲 我是怎么把那没用律师的蛋给切下来的!\N{\fs38}Danny, tell Pedro how I cut that lawyer's balls off!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.98,0:27:35.07,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,沃多夫? 我从来没去过沃多夫\N{\fs38}The Warldorf? I've never been Warldorf.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.34,0:27:39.89,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那群白鬼使唤我们过去 尽干些通马桶的重活累活\N{\fs38}The whites wouldn't let me in unless they full of the shit out the toilets!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.09,0:27:45.17,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,丹尼 当心!\N{\fs38}Watch out, Danny!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.15,0:27:53.24,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,- 丹尼! - 快过去看看!\N{\fs38}- Danny! - Run, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.68,0:27:54.88,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,丹尼!\N{\fs38}Danny!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.60,0:28:04.15,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,- 让路 让我过去看看 - 快叫医生\N{\fs38}- Get out the way, let me see. - Call a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.22,0:28:07.01,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,叫医生 快点\N{\fs38}The doctor, quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.18,0:28:09.23,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,丹尼 你个福大命大的家伙 说话啊\N{\fs38}Danny, you bloody cow. Talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.55,0:28:14.43,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,也就是轻轻拍了一下而已 伙计们\N{\fs38}Ain't nothing but a pat on the back, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.88,0:28:17.84,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,坚持住 医生就快来了\N{\fs38}Hang on, the doctor's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.42,0:28:21.38,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,克劳... 克劳... 克劳斯... 医... 医生\N{\fs38}D... Doctor Kla... Kla... Klaus...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.26,0:28:28.31,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,克劳... 克劳斯曼医生!\N{\fs38}Klau... Klauserman!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.19,0:28:36.32,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那个反正名字很长又很绕口的那个医生...\N{\fs38}Klausermanspizwegensfrischerri... Kemmanschov...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.69,0:28:41.10,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"快枪手"\N{\fs38}Quick on the Trigger
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.29,0:28:47.59,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,超越了"神枪手"...\N{\fs38}lead over Holy Shoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.45,0:28:54.75,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"美好时光"\N{\fs38}and Times Were Good
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.85,0:28:59.50,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,被取消了比赛资格\N{\fs38}was disqualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.39,0:29:06.64,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"坏脾气"\N{\fs38}Saucy Bossy
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.72,0:29:17.98,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,没能超越"勇敢胜者"...\N{\fs38}ain't a soon tooker was Brave Victory, over...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.09,0:29:23.47,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,丹尼那老家伙 躺了三天才归西\N{\fs38}It took him three days to go toes up, old Danny.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.27,0:29:27.13,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那时候是芝加哥第六次比赛\N{\fs38}He let go on the sixth race in Chicago,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.53,0:29:31.39,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"饮用水"赢了"蔬菜汤"两个马身\N{\fs38}Drinkable Water by two lengths over Vegetable Soup,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.41,0:29:34.51,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,赢了"蓝地基"五个马身\N{\fs38}and five over Blue Foudation.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.82,0:29:39.08,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"我虽然行过死荫的幽谷\N{\fs38}"Yea, though I walk through the valley of the shadow of death
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.18,0:29:40.29,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,也不怕遭害 因为你与我同在..."\N{\fs38}I will fear no evil for Thou art with me..."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.29,0:29:43.38,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,反正就是那个名字很长又绕口的医生\N{\fs38}Dr. Klausermanspizwegensdorfentage
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.55,0:29:46.72,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,觉得如果丹尼没笑得这么多的话\N{\fs38}declared that if Danny hadn't laugh so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.88,0:29:49.62,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他很可能会痊愈的\N{\fs38}he probably would have recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.72,0:29:51.96,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但历史没有如果之说\N{\fs38}But history isn't made of "ifs".
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.51,0:29:55.27,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,如今我们唯一能肯定的是\N{\fs38}And the only thing we can say for sure
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.37,0:29:56.89,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,突然间\N{\fs38}is that suddenly,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.36,0:30:02.39,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,莱蒙·1900又一次变成了一名孤儿\N{\fs38}Lemon Nineteen Hundred became an orphan for the second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.39,0:30:07.09,Default-微软雅黑 粗,,0,0,0,,谢谢丹尼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.32,0:30:15.38,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,依圣父圣子和圣灵的名义\N{\fs38}In the name of the Father and of the Son, and of the Holy Ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.38,0:30:17.01,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,阿门\N{\fs38}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.24,0:30:33.85,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,在放音乐哦\N{\fs38}Music.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.03,0:30:48.86,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那时候1900仅仅八岁\N{\fs38}Nineteen Hundred was eight years old then.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.96,0:30:56.06,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我估计 欧美大陆他跑了不下五十来回\N{\fs38}He'd made the trip between Europe and America about fifty times, I imaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.16,0:31:00.53,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,大海就是他的故乡\N{\fs38}The ocean was his home.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.09,0:31:07.26,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那肯定 他闭眼能识路 双手已成蹼!\N{\fs38}Yeah, and his skin was covered in scales and he had two fins, instead of arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.36,0:31:09.60,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我是说真的 老爷子\N{\fs38}It's all true, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.29,0:31:12.01,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,身家性命来担保\N{\fs38}You can bet your soul on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.01,0:31:13.53,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,可这太说不通啊!\N{\fs38}But that's absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.55,0:31:14.79,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,千真万确!\N{\fs38}The God's truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.84,0:31:18.08,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他从来没踏上陆地过 从来没有\N{\fs38}He never set foot on dry land. Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.68,0:31:24.64,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他从海港看了这片大陆千百次 但从来没下过船\N{\fs38}He'd seen it from the ports a hundred times, but he never got off the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.31,0:31:30.18,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,问题就在于 全世界都不会到他的存在\N{\fs38}Problem was as far as the world was concerned he didn't even exist,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.28,0:31:35.47,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,世上没有一个城市 教区 医院 监狱甚至棒球队\N{\fs38}there wasn't a city, a parish, a hospital, jail or baseball team
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.57,0:31:38.55,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,存有过他的痕迹\N{\fs38}that had his name any place.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.65,0:31:43.33,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他没有国籍 没有生日 也没有家人\N{\fs38}He didn't have a country, he didn't even have a birth date. No family.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.15,0:31:50.01,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,虽然已经八岁 但现实意义上 他却从来没出生过\N{\fs38}He was eight years old, but officially, he had never even been born.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.23,0:32:16.83,Default-微软雅黑 粗,,0,0,0,,禁止入内
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.54,0:33:45.75,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,美国!\N{\fs38}America!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.42,0:33:47.75,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,美国!\N{\fs38}America!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.89,0:34:07.65,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这可是绑架罪\N{\fs38}It's kidnapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.81,0:34:11.02,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,如果有一天 那孩子的家人来找他了\N{\fs38}Charges of kidnapping could be brought against you, Captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.19,0:34:14.69,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这绑架的罪名可是要追加到你头上的 船长\N{\fs38}if one fine day the boy's kin were to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.86,0:34:17.91,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,已经过去八年了 我怀疑不会有人来了\N{\fs38}After eight years, I seriously doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.07,0:34:23.58,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但是 我觉得也是时候让那孩子有个正常的人生了\N{\fs38}However, I think the time has come to allow the boy to have a normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.74,0:34:30.79,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我已经起草了一份私人信件 请你替我送到孤儿院\N{\fs38}I've written a personal note which I'd ask you to deliver the head of state orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.96,0:34:34.28,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,好的 船长 那我去哪儿找这孩子呢?\N{\fs38}Very well, Captain. Now where will we find the lad?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.66,0:34:37.24,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,水手长 给他们带路\N{\fs38}Boatswain, show these gentlemen the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.28,0:34:47.69,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,往前\N{\fs38}Forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.69,0:34:49.58,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他们在找1900\N{\fs38}They are looking for 1900.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.68,0:34:51.63,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他们不翻个遍是找不到的\N{\fs38}They got to find the entire space.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.40,0:35:02.84,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,靠边站\N{\fs38}Stand aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.94,0:35:05.37,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,说你呢! 把车停下!\N{\fs38}You there! Hold that cargo!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.47,0:35:06.92,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,所有东西都要搜\N{\fs38}I'm going to search everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.49,0:35:16.58,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,- 你见到过一个小男孩吗? - 我从来没见过\N{\fs38}- Have you seen a little boy? - I never saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.03,0:35:22.69,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,22天后 维吉尼亚号出发前往里约热内卢\N{\fs38}22 days later, when the Virginian headed for Rio de Janeiro,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.79,0:35:27.92,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,没人能找到1900 没有人知道他去哪儿了\N{\fs38}nobody had found Nineteen Hundred, one hadn't a clue guess what happened to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.13,0:35:30.38,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,大家都担心他会出事\N{\fs38}Everybody, they had death in their hearts,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.48,0:35:33.61,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,虽然没有人说出口\N{\fs38}because they had all gotten attached to the little boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.88,0:35:36.03,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但是他们或多或少都记挂这孩子\N{\fs38}although no-one would say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.49,0:35:41.93,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,船长... 醒醒!\N{\fs38}Captain... Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.93,0:35:43.57,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,让我再睡一会儿\N{\fs38}Let me sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.60,0:35:45.53,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,船长 事态紧急!\N{\fs38}Captain, this is emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.53,0:35:46.56,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,天啊!\N{\fs38}Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.56,0:35:48.13,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,船要沉了? 要沉船了!\N{\fs38}We are sinking? We are sinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.23,0:35:51.22,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,更糟! 更糟!\N{\fs38}Worse! Much worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.80,0:36:41.22,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他叫什么名字?\N{\fs38}What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.32,0:36:42.99,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,1900\N{\fs38}Nineteen Hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.02,0:36:46.43,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,不是问这首歌 是那男孩\N{\fs38}Not the song, the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.43,0:36:47.86,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,1900\N{\fs38}Nineteen Hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.40,0:36:50.27,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,如歌一般!\N{\fs38}Like the song!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.22,0:36:59.15,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,史密斯船长那时心里有千万个问题\N{\fs38}He would have wanted to ask him a lot of questions that moment Captain Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.15,0:37:02.44,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,例如"你弹钢琴师到底是从哪儿学的?"\N{\fs38}Like "Where the hell did you learn to play the piano?"
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.54,0:37:05.58,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,或者"你之前到底藏在哪个萝卜坑里了?"\N{\fs38}Or "ln what damn hole have you been hiding?"
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.68,0:37:09.73,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,亦或者"你这首曲子又是从哪里学来的?\N{\fs38}Or "Where in Christ's name are you getting this music from?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.73,0:37:13.78,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,弹得发自内心 毫不刻意"\N{\fs38}Which seems to enter your veins without you even realizing it."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.00,0:37:16.40,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但他毕竟是有身份的人\N{\fs38}But he But he was a man in uniform,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.50,0:37:19.66,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他所能说的唯一的话就是\N{\fs38}and the only thing he managed to say
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.76,0:37:24.74,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,1900 你这样做完全违反了船员规定啊\N{\fs38}Nineteen Hundred, all of this is entirely against the regulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.33,0:37:29.39,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,去他的规定!\N{\fs38}Fuck the regulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.39,0:37:34.48,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,一字不差 "去他的规定"!\N{\fs38}His exact words "Fuck the regulations!"
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.99,0:37:44.79,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但我还不明白 这唱片跟你说的有什么关系\N{\fs38}But I don't understand what the record has to do with any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.64,0:37:49.96,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,老爷子 你的脑子还转的不够快啊\N{\fs38}You're not the sharpest knife in the drawer, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.99,0:37:51.97,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这是他的音乐\N{\fs38}That's his music.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.20,0:37:58.05,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这其实就是丹尼·博德曼·T·D·莱蒙·1900的音乐\N{\fs38}The music of Danny Boodman T.D. Lemon Nineteen Hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.15,0:38:02.28,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,七大洋中那孤傲的象牙之塔\N{\fs38}The greatest ivory tickleron the seven seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.98,0:38:07.03,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这太神奇了!\N{\fs38}Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.06,0:38:12.60,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,所以... 如果你说的是真的话 这唱片简直价值连城啊!\N{\fs38}So... if that's all true, this record must be worth a fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.86,0:38:17.86,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这唱片能让我俩一夜暴富啊\N{\fs38}This record can make us both rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.27,0:38:22.15,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这唱片不应该留存在世\N{\fs38}That record shouldn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.91,0:38:27.66,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,唯一的一张唱片刚刻录完就毁掉了\N{\fs38}The only existing matrix was destroyed right after it was cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.18,0:38:34.10,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那就是这一张了\N{\fs38}Well, this is a matrix.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.95,0:38:41.05,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这唱片现唱现录起来还是蛮好用的\N{\fs38}Quite handy for on-the-spot recordings that sort of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.84,0:38:49.78,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你这东西哪里收来的?\N{\fs38}How did you get your hands on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.05,0:38:57.97,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我可是花了大心思把这些碎片拼成型的\N{\fs38}I spend the better part of the day putting the bits and pieces together.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.38,0:39:04.17,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,找到它纯属意外 它被藏在其中那个钢琴之中\N{\fs38}I found them by accident. Hidden inside one of those two pianos.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.57,0:39:23.03,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我也是从二手商贩那里淘来的\N{\fs38}I bought them from a second-hand dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.39,0:39:28.10,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,普利茅斯当局正清理一艘旧船\N{\fs38}They've emptied out an old hospital ship down at Plymouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.36,0:39:49.20,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,当局过几天就准备把船给处理掉\N{\fs38}They're going to destroy it in a couple of days.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.68,0:39:57.76,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,什么叫"处理掉"?\N{\fs38}What do you mean "destroy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.33,0:40:09.84,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那艘旧船停在哪里?\N{\fs38}Where's the old hospital ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.94,0:40:11.92,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就在那边\N{\fs38}It's over there, mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.18,0:40:13.59,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs38}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.92,0:41:16.36,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,慢点... 滑轮转得慢一点\N{\fs38}Slow down... Not so fast with that pulley.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.72,0:41:21.63,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,当心! 里面装的东西可不是闹着玩的\N{\fs38}Watch that! These aren't bananas, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.40,0:41:25.27,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,当心点 当心点\N{\fs38}Easy up there, easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.90,0:41:50.71,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,哪儿人?\N{\fs38}Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.71,0:41:51.91,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,利物浦\N{\fs38}Liverpool.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.91,0:41:53.52,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,- 你做什么? - 我是剃头的\N{\fs38}- What do you do? - I'm a barber.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.52,0:41:55.59,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,- 准他上船 - 非常感谢\N{\fs38}- Sign him on. - Thanks very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.65,0:41:58.41,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,下一个 你干什么的?\N{\fs38}Next. What's your trade?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.70,0:42:01.87,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我会做木匠 做饭也行 剃头也在行...\N{\fs38}I'm a carpenter, a cook, a barber...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.87,0:42:04.16,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,太复杂 滚蛋!\N{\fs38}Too many things for our test. Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.16,0:42:07.07,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,- 我还能做机械工 - 出去! 下一个\N{\fs38}- I'm also a good mechanic. - Get out! Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.93,0:42:09.21,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你做什么的?\N{\fs38}What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.51,0:42:11.94,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我会吹喇叭\N{\fs38}I play the trumpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.04,0:42:15.43,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,搞音乐我们有人了 下一个\N{\fs38}We've already got musicians on board. Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.57,0:42:17.77,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,出去!\N{\fs38}Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.16,0:42:46.92,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他在干什么?\N{\fs38}Where the hell's he going?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.97,0:43:35.13,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这算什么?\N{\fs38}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.23,0:43:36.43,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs38}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.70,0:43:41.25,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,不懂的东西 那就是爵士乐!\N{\fs38}When you don't know what it is, it's jazz!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.65,0:43:42.64,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,爵士!\N{\fs38}Jazz!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.78,0:43:44.23,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字?\N{\fs38}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.33,0:43:46.16,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我叫马克斯·托尼 先生\N{\fs38}Max Tooney, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.26,0:43:47.96,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,好的!\N{\fs38}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.86,0:44:03.62,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那天是我最开心的一天\N{\fs38}It was the happiest day of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.72,0:44:06.44,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,所有人眼中都充满了希望\N{\fs38}All those peoplewith hope in their eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.54,0:44:09.17,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那道别的场面 船笛长鸣...\N{\fs38}The goodbyes, the sirens...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.17,0:44:12.68,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这个大家伙开始了它的旅程\N{\fs38}and that big floating world starting to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.72,0:44:17.53,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那感觉就是一个大派对 一切喧闹都为我助威\N{\fs38}It felt like one big party, a huge bash just for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.75,0:44:22.47,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但仅仅三天之后 大海就厌倦那份喧嚣嘈闹\N{\fs38}But just three days later the ocean got tired of the festivities.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.57,0:44:29.26,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,突然某天夜里 大海一反温柔常态 狂暴的海浪似乎摧毁一切\N{\fs38}Suddenly, in the middle of the night, she went berserk and all hell broke loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.52,0:44:34.39,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,对于一个吹喇叭的汉子面对狂风大浪\N{\fs38}Now, a guy blowing a trumpet on a ship
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.49,0:44:37.34,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,实在没有多少办法\N{\fs38}can't do much when there's a raging storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.34,0:44:42.03,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,当时不吹喇叭对他来说是唯一能做的事情 起码没有将情况复杂化\N{\fs38}Not playing the trumpet is about the only thing you can do just not to complicate matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.43,0:44:44.63,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就算这样我也快受不了了\N{\fs38}But I couldn't bear being down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.73,0:44:47.08,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,一首歌词不停在我脑中翻转\N{\fs38}Same line kept raging in my brain:
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.18,0:44:49.23,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"如老鼠般死去"\N{\fs38}"he died like a rat."
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.43,0:44:56.88,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但我最不想发生的事情 就是死的跟老鼠一样窝囊\N{\fs38}And the last thing I wanted was to die like a rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.07,0:45:21.44,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,奶奶的 我竟然迷路了!\N{\fs38}Damn it, I'm lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.10,0:45:57.44,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,嘿 小号手? 你怎么了?\N{\fs38}Hey, Conn? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.91,0:45:59.90,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,晕船了吗?\N{\fs38}Lose your sea legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.32,0:46:02.89,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你是新来的那个吹喇叭的 对吧?\N{\fs38}You're the new trumpet man, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.89,0:46:04.33,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,而你抱着个坛子干嘛?\N{\fs38}And you blow a can?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.99,0:46:12.14,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,跟我来 我会让你感觉好点\N{\fs38}Come with me. I have a cure for your misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.08,0:46:14.32,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,跟我来\N{\fs38}Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.46,0:46:52.88,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,麻烦把琴刹关了\N{\fs38}Take the brakes off, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.88,0:46:55.43,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,什么... 你疯了吧!\N{\fs38}What... That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.06,0:46:59.58,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,相信我 把琴刹给关了\N{\fs38}Trust me. Just take the brakes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.90,0:47:16.78,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,坐我旁边\N{\fs38}Hop on next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.56,0:47:19.91,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你什么情况 脑子烧糊涂了吧\N{\fs38}What are you, some kind of nut case.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.01,0:47:22.74,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,要么快点上来 不然就没机会了\N{\fs38}You better get on now or you never will.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.51,0:47:56.86,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,告诉我 你有孩子吗?\N{\fs38}Tell me something, do you have children?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.02,0:48:01.38,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,好吧 他们就应该把你关进孤儿院!\N{\fs38}Shit, they'll lock you up in the orphanage one of these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.48,0:48:02.89,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他疯了吧\N{\fs38}He's nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.95,0:48:09.93,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,哇哈 老妈!\N{\fs38}Whoa, Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.03,0:48:11.90,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,原来你还懂马啊!\N{\fs38}I see you know your horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.91,0:48:13.29,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,一点点而已\N{\fs38}Just a litte.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.33,0:48:14.55,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮!\N{\fs38}Good man!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.76,0:48:29.84,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这感觉就像大海在跟我们较劲一般\N{\fs38}It was like the sea was rocking us.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.15,0:48:33.12,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但当我们任钢琴四处滑动\N{\fs38}And while we were floating around the colorants
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.12,0:48:35.30,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,跟那些家具灯具转圈的时候\N{\fs38}and brushing the lamps and furniture,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.30,0:48:40.27,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我发现 其实我们是在跟大海跳着舞\N{\fs38}I realised that what we were really doing was dancing with the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.27,0:48:43.14,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我们和她 一对疯狂的舞者\N{\fs38}Us and her, crazy dancers,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.24,0:48:48.27,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,随着轻快地华尔兹在金色大厅中缓缓旋转\N{\fs38}locked in a joyful waltzon the golden parquet of night.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.70,0:49:49.53,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,晚上好 船长\N{\fs38}Good evening, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.19,0:49:52.68,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,要搭一程吗?\N{\fs38}Care for a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.78,0:49:54.10,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,1900!\N{\fs38}Nineteen Hundred!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.10,0:49:55.97,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我就猜到是你!\N{\fs38}I should know it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.07,0:49:59.56,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,不然船上有谁敢做这种发神经的事情?\N{\fs38}Who else on this ship would do anything as lunatic as this?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.56,0:50:01.18,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,除了你没别人! 说你呢 1900!\N{\fs38}Except you! Nineteen Hundred!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.28,0:50:03.23,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我只是在做实验而已 先生\N{\fs38}I was just experimenting, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.79,0:50:06.11,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,下次我会注意一点的\N{\fs38}When I get kings up,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.21,0:50:08.45,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我保证不会有类似的事情发生了\N{\fs38}I'm sure you nothing among this will never happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.31,0:50:14.73,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,没错 其实就是琴刹不见了而已 真不巧!\N{\fs38}Yeah, it's missed brakes should fix those. Grace!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.41,0:50:23.67,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,再跟我说说 那窗户有多大来着?\N{\fs38}Tell me again how big the fucking window was?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.67,0:50:25.34,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,反正那窗户超级大!\N{\fs38}What a big fucking window!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.59,0:50:31.61,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 我们这辈子估计都要铲煤了\N{\fs38}You know, we're going to be shoveling coal on this ship till eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.71,0:50:33.46,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,可不是吗!\N{\fs38}No shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.56,0:50:52.19,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,起码你知道你长大会做什么了!\N{\fs38}Least you know what you'll be doing when you grow up!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.22,0:50:59.77,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 小号手 - 怎么了?\N{\fs38}- Hey, Conn. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.66,0:51:02.38,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你是新奥尔良人 对吧?\N{\fs38}You're from New Orleans, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.40,0:51:03.77,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道的?\N{\fs38}How did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.42,0:51:07.27,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我最喜欢那镇子了\N{\fs38}I love that town.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.30,0:51:10.43,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,真的吗? 我已经好久没回去过了\N{\fs38}Really? I haven't been there in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.55,0:51:14.22,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,冬天的时候 那里多漂亮\N{\fs38}In winter, it's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.58,0:51:18.63,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,三月的时候\N{\fs38}And in March,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.79,0:51:26.30,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,当你防不胜防的时候 大雾突然而至\N{\fs38}you can always count on one afternoon when you least expect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.50,0:51:31.33,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那大雾浓密的如同牛奶一般\N{\fs38}The fog slides in a milky barrier
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.86,0:51:37.53,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就悬浮在路灯下面 黑压压地罩住一切!\N{\fs38}hangs just below the street lamps.It cuts everything off!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.49,0:51:42.77,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就像白色利刃 一切宛如仙境!\N{\fs38}Like a white blade. And it's magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.76,0:51:49.60,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,房子的顶层看不见了 大树的枝桠也看不见了\N{\fs38}Houses lose their top floors, trees lose their branches,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.97,0:51:56.06,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,看不见圣路易斯大教堂的侧踏 也看不见过路人的脑袋\N{\fs38}St. Louis Cathedral loses its spires, people passing by they lose their heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.16,0:52:00.10,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,反正脖子以上的部位 什么都看不见了\N{\fs38}So from the neck up everything disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.98,0:52:04.36,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你在杰克森广场所能看到的就是一群没脑袋的行人\N{\fs38}All you can see in Jackson Squareis a bunch of decapitated bodies,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.37,0:52:07.83,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,睁眼瞎地四处乱撞\N{\fs38}stumbling around and bumping into each other
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.00,0:52:10.05,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"你走路不看路的吗?"\N{\fs38}"How's your mama and them?"
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.66,0:52:15.25,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,没错! 只可惜没过多久雾就散了\N{\fs38}That's it! Too bad it doesn't last long.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.75,0:52:17.82,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但你怎么会知道这些事情的?\N{\fs38}But how do you know all these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.27,0:52:25.06,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,话说\N{\fs38}You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.23,0:52:31.69,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,自从我坐上这船 我就听说有这么一个人\N{\fs38}ever since I came on board, I been hearing a lot of talk about a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.92,0:52:36.26,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他在这地方跟乔治亚火车货运公司一样出名\N{\fs38}He got this name runs on like a Georgia freight train.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.88,0:52:43.03,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他好像就生养在这船上 从来没下船过\N{\fs38}He's supposed to have been born on this ship and never been off it since.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.33,0:52:45.08,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,很离奇的故事\N{\fs38}Crazy story.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.38,0:52:48.47,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,二十年了都没下过船?\N{\fs38}Twenty years without ever setting foot on land?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.47,0:52:49.62,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,二十七年了\N{\fs38}Twenty-seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.62,0:52:54.15,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他们还说 那家伙的音乐 大家都没听到过\N{\fs38}They say this guy makes music that's never been heard before.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.15,0:52:55.70,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我也听说过这号人\N{\fs38}I've heard of him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.80,0:53:00.40,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,一开始 我还以为你就是那个人\N{\fs38}First off, I thought you were the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.43,0:53:03.46,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,- 但有些事说不通 - 当然了\N{\fs38}- But then something didn't add up. - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.46,0:53:04.71,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我觉得\N{\fs38}I figure,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.71,0:53:10.19,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,如果他是1900的话 他怎么对新奥尔良这么了解?\N{\fs38}if he's Nineteen Hundred how could he know New Orleans so well?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.29,0:53:14.23,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,肯定是因为他去过新奥尔良\N{\fs38}Because you've been to New Orleans.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.24,0:53:18.11,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,如果我告诉你 我从来没去过那地方 你相信我吗?\N{\fs38}If I told you I'd never set foot in that town, would you believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.26,0:53:28.09,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,不管你是何方神圣 我是马克斯·托尼\N{\fs38}Whoever you are, Max Tooney.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.36,0:53:30.53,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,很高兴认识你\N{\fs38}Glad to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.05,0:53:47.73,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,情况怎么样了?\N{\fs38}How we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.83,0:53:50.41,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,应该动手炸船了\N{\fs38}We're supposed to blow it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.51,0:53:54.06,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,别等这船被鱼蛀空了才动手!\N{\fs38}Not wait for it to be eaten by the fishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.10,0:53:59.48,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我们快好了 装上最后一根引线就好了\N{\fs38}We're almost done, just laying the last charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.91,0:54:06.47,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你这是要去哪里?\N{\fs38}Where the hell are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.50,0:54:07.94,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,- 我要去见一个人 - 拦住他!\N{\fs38}- I have to look for someone. - Stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.94,0:54:10.79,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,其实...\N{\fs38}It's not eazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.79,0:54:12.84,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,给我下去...\N{\fs38}Get down there...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.24,0:54:18.49,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你们这群混蛋 让我上船!\N{\fs38}You bastards, let me on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.29,0:54:24.91,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你能再说一遍吗? 我觉得第一次没听明白\N{\fs38}Could you run that by me again? I don't think I got the straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.01,0:54:26.86,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,绝对的 我重复一遍\N{\fs38}You bet. I'll run that by you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.96,0:54:32.22,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你不能把船给炸了 因为我最好的朋友还在船上\N{\fs38}You're not going to blow up a goddamn thing, because my best friend's on this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.84,0:54:34.94,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你们炸船就等于谋杀\N{\fs38}You'll all be responsible for murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.97,0:54:36.15,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,轰他出去\N{\fs38}Get him out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.15,0:54:38.80,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我不管你怎么做 把他轰出去就行!\N{\fs38}Do whatever you want, but get him off my case!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.83,0:54:41.46,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这事不是我编出来的 我没疯\N{\fs38}I'm not making this up and I'm not crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.46,0:54:43.87,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,如果我告诉你还有人在维吉尼亚号上\N{\fs38}If I tell you there's a man aboard the Virginian,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.87,0:54:47.38,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,看在上帝的份上 那就是有人在上面!\N{\fs38}Jesus Christ, it means there's a man aboard the Virginian.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.40,0:54:51.67,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我们从船头清理到船尾 连一个门把手都没放过\N{\fs38}We cleaned that scuttle from stem to stern. Not even doorknobs were left.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.67,0:54:54.01,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,只有炸药 炸药! 非常多的炸弹\N{\fs38}Only dynamite. Dynamite! Lots of dynamite.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.01,0:54:55.90,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你凭什么这么确定这船上还有人?\N{\fs38}How can you be so sure that's a man on board?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.91,0:54:57.63,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,如有你有真凭实据 拿出来\N{\fs38}If you've any proof, out with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.64,0:55:00.33,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,因为最终还是要我引爆那堆炸药的\N{\fs38}Because I'm the horse's ass who has to throw that switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.34,0:55:01.92,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我确定他就在上面\N{\fs38}I'm sure he's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.29,0:55:06.81,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我毕竟在维吉尼亚号待了好多年\N{\fs38}I spent the best years of my life on the Virginian.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.81,0:55:14.32,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你在三等舱那边了发现一架立式钢琴吗?\N{\fs38}Did you find an upright piano in third class?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.81,0:55:21.49,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,维吉尼亚号是世上唯一一艘三等舱配有钢琴的邮轮\N{\fs38}The Virginian is the only ship in the world with a piano in third class.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.69,0:55:25.58,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你们到底有没有在三等舱找到一架立式钢琴?\N{\fs38}Was there or wasn't there an upright piano in third class?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.68,0:55:29.80,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,的确有架钢琴 但不是立式的 是三角钢琴\N{\fs38}Well, there was a piano in third class, but it was not upright. It was horizontal.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.82,0:55:31.42,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就算是圆形钢琴\N{\fs38}Even it was round,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.42,0:55:34.79,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我还是不明白这钢琴跟船上藏着个人有什么关系\N{\fs38}I don't see what the hell is the goddamned piano got to do with a ghost aboard that ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.89,0:55:38.15,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那艘旧船里面少说也藏着千百个孤魂野鬼!\N{\fs38}There's thousands of poor dead souls hanging out of that hospital ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.25,0:55:41.38,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,给我滚出去 不然我就叫警察了\N{\fs38}Get out of my sight, or I'll call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.48,0:55:43.53,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,把你的手拿开!\N{\fs38}You kick off your hands off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.16,0:55:45.38,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,听着...\N{\fs38}Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.38,0:55:51.01,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你所谓的那些孤魂野鬼里面 藏着世上最伟大的钢琴师!\N{\fs38}amongst those thousands of dead souls is the greatest piano player in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.01,0:55:53.59,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,可船上一个活人都没有啊!\N{\fs38}Yet don't a bleeding piano player!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.59,0:55:56.30,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,话说你在维吉尼亚号上这么多年都干了什么?\N{\fs38}And what were you doing all those years aboard the Virginian?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.31,0:55:57.78,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,调琴弦吗?\N{\fs38}Tuning the strings?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.15,0:56:00.40,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我在维吉尼亚号上干嘛?\N{\fs38}What was I doing on the Virginian?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.92,0:56:04.44,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你做了些什么?\N{\fs38}What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.57,0:56:13.38,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我可是登台演奏的!\N{\fs38}I played!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.54,0:56:16.15,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,女士们 先生们\N{\fs38}Ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.19,0:56:17.94,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,女士们 先生们(德语)\N{\fs38}Meine Damen und Herren,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.04,0:56:20.13,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,女士们 先生们(意大利语)\N{\fs38}Signore e signori,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.13,0:56:21.53,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,女士们 先生们(法语)\N{\fs38}Mesdames et Messieurs,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.54,0:56:24.99,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,比尔·道格拉斯在此欢迎您乘坐弗吉尼亚号\N{\fs38}Bill Douglas here to welcomes you aboard the Virginian.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.09,0:56:30.76,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,并希望您在大西洋爵士乐队的陪伴下 度过愉快的夜晚!\N{\fs38}And wishes you a pleasant evening in the accompany of the Atlantic Jazz Band !
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.85,0:56:36.68,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,太棒了!\N{\fs38}Perfetto!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.95,0:56:43.71,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,1900 拜托了 弹点正常曲调 行吗?\N{\fs38}Please, Nineteen Hundred, just the normal notes. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.54,0:56:59.46,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我们演奏 是因为大海浩瀚而可怕\N{\fs38}We played because the ocean is big and scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.56,0:57:02.50,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我们演奏 能使人们感觉不到时间的流逝\N{\fs38}We played so that people wouldn't feel the time passing
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.50,0:57:05.31,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,忘记身在何处 自己是谁\N{\fs38}and could forget where and who they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.31,0:57:07.65,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我们演奏 他们起舞\N{\fs38}We played to make them dance,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.75,0:57:12.57,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,舞蹈的时候充满了活力 就像上帝一样\N{\fs38}because when you dance you can't die and you feel like God.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.67,0:57:14.44,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我们演奏拉格泰姆乐\N{\fs38}We played ragtime,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.44,0:57:18.18,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,无人注视的时候 上帝也是跟着它起舞的\N{\fs38}because that's the music God dances to,when nobody's watching him,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.18,0:57:20.29,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,如果上帝是黑人的话!\N{\fs38}assuming that God is black!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.57,0:57:26.63,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,收工啦 伙计们!\N{\fs38}End of the line boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.20,0:57:33.58,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,上帝呀 我一定是罪孽深重啊 是这样吗 上帝?\N{\fs38}Jesus, I must be a real sinner. Is that it, God?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.60,0:57:51.73,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,看他多出色呀!\N{\fs38}Right! Look he'd done!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.55,0:57:54.32,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,棒极了!\N{\fs38}It's sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.63,0:58:23.61,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,在三等舱里\N{\fs38}But it was in third class
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.63,0:58:27.50,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,1900演奏着属于他自己的音乐\N{\fs38}that Nineteen Hundred played the music which was really his.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.60,0:58:30.75,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,无数个下午和夜晚\N{\fs38}He'd go in the afternoons or late at night,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.75,0:58:33.68,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他从不用正常的曲调弹奏\N{\fs38}when he didn't have to play the normal notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.69,0:58:38.19,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他的曲子包含了非比寻常的各种元素\N{\fs38}And his music was made of notes that were everything but normal.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.07,1:00:06.65,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你弹琴的时候 在想什么呢?\N{\fs38}What the hell do you think about when you're playing?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.75,1:00:10.28,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,弹琴的时候 你的思绪在何处?\N{\fs38}Where does your mind go when you hit the keys?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.28,1:00:14.13,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,昨晚 我身处一个美丽的国度\N{\fs38}Last night I was in a beautiful country.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.47,1:00:19.07,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,女人的头发上喷了香水 一切都五彩斑斓\N{\fs38}Women had perfume in their hair. Everything glowed.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.22,1:00:21.22,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,到处都是老虎\N{\fs38}And it was full of tigers.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.68,1:00:23.33,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他神游着\N{\fs38}He traveled.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.35,1:00:26.16,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,每次他都去不同的地方\N{\fs38}And each time he ended up some place different.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.16,1:00:30.13,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,有时在伦敦中心 有时在经过乡村中部的火车上\N{\fs38}In the heart of London, on a train in the middle of the country,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.13,1:00:32.37,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,有时身处巨大火山的边缘\N{\fs38}on the edge of a giant volcano,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.47,1:00:35.53,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,有时在世界上最大的教堂里\N{\fs38}in the biggest church in the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.53,1:00:39.97,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,数着教堂外的横杆 注视着十字架\N{\fs38}counting the columns and staring up at the crucifixes.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.95,1:00:42.65,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他周游四方\N{\fs38}He travelled.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.28,1:00:46.75,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,哥们 弹一首塔朗泰拉舞曲吧!\N{\fs38}Guaglio', facci sentire una bella tarantella!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.81,1:00:49.99,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那请你说说塔朗泰拉舞曲怎么弹吧!\N{\fs38}E tu fammi capire come fa questa tarantella, paisa'!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.61,1:01:15.93,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,下船后 人们会议论这奇特的音乐\N{\fs38}The people getting off the ship would talk about a strange music
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.93,1:01:21.66,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,也会谈起仿佛有四只手同时在弹琴的钢琴家\N{\fs38}and a pianist who looked like he had four hands, for all the notes he was hit.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.26,1:01:33.68,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,怪诞的故事被流传着 有些却是真的\N{\fs38}Weird tales circulated, some even true.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.89,1:01:36.87,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,比如有个叫威尔逊的美国参议员\N{\fs38}Like the one about an American senator named Wilson,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.07,1:01:39.83,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,曾经来到三等舱\N{\fs38}who used to travel in third class
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.93,1:01:46.36,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就为了聆听丹尼·博德曼·T·D·莱蒙·1900演奏的音乐\N{\fs38}just to hear the music of Danny boodmant.D. Lemon Nineteen Hundred.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.60,1:01:59.58,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,美国!\N{\fs38}America!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.05,1:02:22.76,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你怎么停了? 继续弹呀\N{\fs38}Why did you stop? Please, continue.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.31,1:02:29.53,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,抱歉 议员 到港了 我只在海上演奏\N{\fs38}I'm sorry, Senator, it made port. I only play on the open sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.63,1:02:30.98,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这太可笑了\N{\fs38}But that's absurd.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.98,1:02:33.34,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,港口对于我来说就是陆地 我不在陆地上演奏\N{\fs38}Ports are land to me.I don't play on land.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.44,1:02:35.59,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你是说 你从未巡演过吗?\N{\fs38}You mean, you've never gone on tour?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.03,1:02:37.27,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,什么意思?\N{\fs38}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.49,1:02:45.18,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,艺术家为了向全世界展示他们的才能 进行的长途旅行啊\N{\fs38}Long trips on which artists display their talents around the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.28,1:02:49.34,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,某种意义上 已经巡演完了 用我自己的方式\N{\fs38}In a sense, that's all I ever done.In my way.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.31,1:02:51.64,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fs38}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.60,1:02:56.24,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,能允许我采访你一下吗?\N{\fs38}Would you grant me an interview?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.13,1:03:02.54,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,采... 什么?\N{\fs38}An inter... what?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.39,1:03:04.51,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,采访?\N{\fs38}An interview?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.68,1:03:06.84,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,什么意思?\N{\fs38}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.09,1:03:09.81,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,议员问:\N{\fs38}The senator asks:
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.81,1:03:15.16,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,回到家乡以后 你想做什么?\N{\fs38}Is there anything you enjoy about when you go back to your home town?"
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.17,1:03:16.83,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,1900回答\N{\fs38}Nineteen Hundred
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.83,1:03:19.81,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我最想在巴黎做的是...\N{\fs38}what I like to do best in Paris is....
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.81,1:03:25.28,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,在埃菲尔铁塔下等日落时 看人们从塔上失足落下\N{\fs38}wait under the Eiffel tower at sunset, for the people who throw themselves off the top
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.28,1:03:29.60,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,在他们完全着地之前\N{\fs38}and try to guess what country they're from by their screams
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.60,1:03:32.95,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,通过他们的尖叫声 分辨他们是哪国人!\N{\fs38}before they go splat all over the ground!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.64,1:03:46.25,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你为什么不下船呢? 一次? 就一次?\N{\fs38}Why the hell don't you get off? Just once? One time?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.48,1:03:52.04,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,亲眼目睹这个世界?\N{\fs38}See the world for yourself with your own eyes?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.41,1:03:57.93,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你想过吗? 你可以做任何事\N{\fs38}You ever think about it? You could do anything you wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.29,1:04:01.36,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,人们会为你痴狂\N{\fs38}People would go crazy for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.59,1:04:05.58,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你能赚很多钱呢 哥们\N{\fs38}You could make beaucoup bucks, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.68,1:04:10.39,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,买上最好的房子 再娶个妻子\N{\fs38}Get yourself the finest house,Get yourself a wife.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.68,1:04:13.04,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,为什么不呢?\N{\fs38}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.28,1:04:25.58,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,上帝知道你的余生无法像溜溜球一样到处旅游\N{\fs38}God knows you can't spend the rest of your life traveling back and forth like some yo-yo.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.68,1:04:30.85,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,世界就在那儿 过了这个踏板就是\N{\fs38}The world is out there. Nothing but a gangplank to cross.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.99,1:04:35.53,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,踏板是什么? 就这几步路\N{\fs38}And what's a gangplank? A few stupid steps.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.53,1:04:39.48,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,跨过这几步 一切都在等待着你\N{\fs38}Christ, everything is waiting at the bottom of those steps.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.01,1:04:42.18,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,为什么你不去呢?\N{\fs38}Why don't you just do it?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.98,1:04:44.47,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就一次\N{\fs38}One time.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.32,1:04:48.05,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,为什么不下船呢?\N{\fs38}Why don't you just get off?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.30,1:04:57.82,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,为什么? 为什么? 为什么?\N{\fs38}Why? Why? Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.13,1:04:59.96,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,怎么那么多为什么?\N{\fs38}Why? Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.04,1:05:05.99,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我想你们陆地上的人\N{\fs38}I think you land people
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.06,1:05:10.20,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,浪费了太多时间在想为什么\N{\fs38}waste a lot of time wondering why.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.55,1:05:14.73,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,冬天来了 期待夏天\N{\fs38}Winter comes and you can't wait for summer.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.73,1:05:17.84,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,夏天来了 又害怕冬天\N{\fs38}Summer comes and you live in dread of winter.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.45,1:05:21.18,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,所以从不厌倦旅行\N{\fs38}That's why you never tire of traveling.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.29,1:05:26.74,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,总是追逐遥远的 四季如夏的地方\N{\fs38}Always chasing someplace far away where it's always summer.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.57,1:05:32.46,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,听起来不适合我\N{\fs38}Doesn't sound like a good bet to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.37,1:05:48.61,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,住手 快住手!\N{\fs38}Hold it, stop everything!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.71,1:05:50.68,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,告诉他们别引爆炸药\N{\fs38}Tell them to lose the detonators.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.68,1:05:52.29,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,别引爆炸药!\N{\fs38}Unhook them!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.32,1:05:54.21,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,出什么事了 头儿?\N{\fs38}What's going on, boss?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.98,1:06:37.07,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我要是你 就诚心祈祷在这堆破烂里能找到人\N{\fs38}If I were you, I'll pray hard we'll find somebody hidden on this paterost.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.07,1:06:41.03,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,有人会把三条腿的螳螂当成钢琴\N{\fs38}Even somebody who can mistake a three-legged cockroach for a piano.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.40,1:06:44.00,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这简直就是大海捞针\N{\fs38}It's like looking for a needle in a haystack.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.64,1:06:49.31,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,先生 我找到了\N{\fs38}Sir, I found it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.75,1:06:52.77,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这曾是他的船舱\N{\fs38}This was his cabin.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.39,1:09:21.27,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,原谅我的情不自禁\N{\fs38}Forgive me for allowing myself to,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.28,1:09:23.90,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你的音乐太优美了\N{\fs38}your music was so strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.45,1:09:32.50,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我想 您来自北意大利吧\N{\fs38}Northern Italy, I'll bet.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.50,1:09:36.15,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,对极了 准确的说是弗留利\N{\fs38}Bravo, Friuli, to be exact.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.15,1:09:38.85,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,朋友 继续弹啊\N{\fs38}But don't stop playing. Suona.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.78,1:09:48.82,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,来根烟吗?\N{\fs38}Want a cicca?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.72,1:09:55.37,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,要去美国了 您看起来一点都不开心\N{\fs38}You don't look too happy to be going to America.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.95,1:09:56.95,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,和去美国无关\N{\fs38}It's not America.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.08,1:10:07.07,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,而是我舍弃的一切\N{\fs38}It's everything I leave behind.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.33,1:10:11.49,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,直到几年前 我还只是井底之蛙\N{\fs38}Until a few years ago I know only my field.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.49,1:10:16.29,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我的世界起始于那一小块地上\N{\fs38}The world for me started and ended there in that little piece of the land.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.37,1:10:19.77,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我从未逛过城市里的大街\N{\fs38}I never walked down the main street of a city.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.39,1:10:23.78,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,也许你无法理解 然而...\N{\fs38}Maybe you can't understand, but....
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.85,1:10:26.88,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我非常理解\N{\fs38}I understand that perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.39,1:10:32.62,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我知道某人有非常相似的经历\N{\fs38}I know someone who went through something very similar.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.65,1:10:35.94,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他的地 有一天也干涸了吗?\N{\fs38}And one fine day did his field go dry, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.38,1:10:39.40,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他的妻子也和牧师跑了吗?\N{\fs38}And did his wife also run off with a priest?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.09,1:10:47.10,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,高烧也夺去了他五个孩子的生命吗?\N{\fs38}And did the fever take his five children?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.89,1:10:50.25,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,没有 但他也孤独一生\N{\fs38}No. But he ended up alone, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.38,1:10:54.71,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那他比我幸运多了\N{\fs38}Then he is more lucky than me
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.57,1:10:58.95,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我还有个小女儿\N{\fs38}I still have a daughter. The young one.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.05,1:11:00.77,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,她活下来了\N{\fs38}She survived.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.19,1:11:07.06,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,为了她 我决定与坏命运抗争\N{\fs38}And it's for her that I decide one day to fight against my bad luck,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.16,1:11:09.62,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,开始了漫无目的的旅行\N{\fs38}and travel all over without a destination.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.79,1:11:18.88,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,一天 当我穿过一个从未去过的小镇\N{\fs38}And then one day, when I go through one of the many towns I never see before,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.28,1:11:24.62,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,登上山坡 我看到了...\N{\fs38}I come to a hill, and then I see...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.62,1:11:27.06,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,一生中最美的东西\N{\fs38}the most beautiful thing in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.50,1:11:29.76,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,大海!\N{\fs38}The sea!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.16,1:11:31.40,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,大海?\N{\fs38}The sea?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.23,1:11:34.21,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我从未见过\N{\fs38}I never see it before.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.36,1:11:38.84,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就像闪电一般触击着我\N{\fs38}It was like lightning hit me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.84,1:11:41.66,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,因为我听到了它的声音\N{\fs38}Because I hear the voice.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.83,1:11:44.28,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,大海的声音?\N{\fs38}The voice of the sea?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.28,1:11:46.36,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,对 大海的声音\N{\fs38}Yeah, the voice of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.16,1:11:51.14,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我从未听过\N{\fs38}I've never heard it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.10,1:11:55.66,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,大海的声音 像是呐喊\N{\fs38}The voice of the sea, it is like a shout.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.70,1:11:58.23,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,呐喊声强壮而有力\N{\fs38}A shout big and strong,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.23,1:12:02.35,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,呐喊着 呼啸着 在呼喊着\N{\fs38}screaming and screaming. And the thing it was screaming
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.88,1:12:04.76,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"你"!\N{\fs38}"You"!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.32,1:12:09.74,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,简直就没长脑子!\N{\fs38}With shit instead brains!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.81,1:12:14.88,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,生命无限 你知道吗?\N{\fs38}Life is immense, can you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.47,1:12:18.44,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"无限啊"!\N{\fs38}"Immense!"
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.90,1:12:23.30,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我从没这样想过 于是一场革命在我脑中爆发了\N{\fs38}I never think of it that way. A revolution was in my head.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.27,1:12:28.93,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,因此我决定改变命运\N{\fs38}That's how I suddenly decide to change my life,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.42,1:12:32.78,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,重新开始\N{\fs38}to start fresh.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.72,1:12:38.55,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,改变命运 重新开始\N{\fs38}Change life. Start fresh.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.65,1:12:40.88,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,记得告诉你的朋友\N{\fs38}Tell that to your friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.06,1:12:44.10,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,1900!\N{\fs38}Nineteen Hundred!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.81,1:12:49.85,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,1900!\N{\fs38}Nineteen Hundred!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.77,1:12:54.30,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我是你的朋友 马克斯·托尼\N{\fs38}It's Max Tooney, your friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.31,1:12:58.90,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,快出来吧 1900! 我也是你的朋友\N{\fs38}Come on out, Nineteen Hundred! I'm your friend, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.91,1:13:03.64,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,虽然我们从未谋面 别担心 没有警察!\N{\fs38}Even if we've never met. Don't worry, no cops!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.95,1:13:24.26,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你说有架钢琴 到底在哪儿?\N{\fs38}You said something about a piano. Where was it exactly?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.26,1:13:26.23,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,在那儿发现的\N{\fs38}We found it over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.74,1:13:34.07,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,1900!\N{\fs38}Nineteen Hundred!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.75,1:13:39.07,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,1900!\N{\fs38}Nineteen Hundred!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.02,1:13:54.12,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,女士们 先生们\N{\fs38}Ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.71,1:13:56.78,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,女士们 先生们(德语)\N{\fs38}Meine Damen und Herren,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.88,1:13:59.24,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,女士们 先生们(意大利语)\N{\fs38}Signore e signori,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.34,1:14:01.74,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,女士们 先生们(法语)\N{\fs38}Mesdames et Messieurs,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.84,1:14:08.85,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,比尔·道格拉斯在此欢迎您乘坐弗吉尼亚号\N{\fs38}Maestro Bill Douglas here, welcoming you on board the Virginian.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.70,1:14:17.16,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,并希望您在大西洋爵士乐队的陪伴下 度过愉快的夜晚!\N{\fs38}Wishing you a very pleasant evening in the accompany of the Atlantic Jazz Band!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.16,1:14:21.44,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,小提琴手 比尔·道格拉斯!\N{\fs38}On the violin yours truly, Bill Douglas!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.30,1:14:25.73,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,大号和贝斯手 弗莱迪·罗亚卡诺!\N{\fs38}Tuba and bass, Freddie Loyacano!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.01,1:14:29.36,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,小号 马克斯·托尼!\N{\fs38}Max Tooney on trumpet!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.14,1:14:35.10,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,长号 吉姆·吉姆·布莱斯·嘉路博!\N{\fs38}Jim Jim Breath Gallupon trombone!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.18,1:14:39.25,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,鼓手 萨姆·斯嘉丽丝!\N{\fs38}Sam Scalisi on the drums!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.04,1:14:45.84,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,萨克斯手 昏睡的萨姆·华盛顿!\N{\fs38}On saxophone, Sam Sleepy Washington!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.36,1:14:49.74,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,五弦琴 奥斯卡·德拉格拉!\N{\fs38}On banjo, Oscar Delaguerra!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.74,1:14:52.91,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,最后隆重介绍 钢琴的演奏者\N{\fs38}And finally, on piano,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.18,1:14:57.03,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,丹尼·博德曼·T·D·莱蒙·1900\N{\fs38}Danny Boodman T.D. Lemon Nineteen Hundred.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.08,1:14:59.12,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他是最棒的!\N{\fs38}The greatest!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.62,1:15:18.41,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,1900 最后一次 拜托了 只弹......\N{\fs38}For the last time Nineteen Hundred, just...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.41,1:15:19.73,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,只弹正常的曲调\N{\fs38}Just the normal notes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.83,1:15:21.97,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你们在干什么? 快坐好!\N{\fs38}What are you doing here? Take your places!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.67,1:15:58.33,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,嘿 收工啦!\N{\fs38}Hey, end of the line!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.02,1:16:10.15,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你真的惹毛我了 你这肮脏司炉工的小孩!\N{\fs38}You've really got over me, you son of a dirty stoker!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.78,1:16:15.84,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,总有一天 大家会不再欣赏你这滑稽的音乐\N{\fs38}One night the public's not going to appreciate your antics.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.84,1:16:17.59,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我发誓 在那晚\N{\fs38}And that night, I swear,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.59,1:16:20.81,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,一定亲手把你扔下船去\N{\fs38}I'm going to throw you overboard myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.10,1:16:46.85,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你是怎么想到的?\N{\fs38}Where do you get it?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.61,1:16:48.71,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,什么?\N{\fs38}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.71,1:16:49.87,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,想弹的曲子\N{\fs38}The music.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.87,1:16:51.11,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\fs38}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.11,1:16:53.21,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这么说 你看到坐那儿的女人了吗?\N{\fs38}You see that woman over there? For example?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.34,1:17:00.68,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,她看起来像在年轻情夫的帮助下\N{\fs38}She looks like someone who's just killed her husband
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.68,1:17:02.38,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,刚谋杀了亲夫\N{\fs38}with the help of her lover.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.78,1:17:04.86,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,现在要带着所有珠宝潜逃了\N{\fs38}And now she's running off with the family jewels.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.02,1:17:07.53,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你不觉得这个音乐在说她吗?\N{\fs38}Don't you think this music's her?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.63,1:17:09.44,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,见鬼 还真是!\N{\fs38}Damn, it's true!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.40,1:17:15.01,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,看见那个男的了吗?\N{\fs38}You see that guy over there?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.61,1:17:18.09,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他无法忘却过去\N{\fs38}He can't forget a thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.15,1:17:21.65,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他的脑海里装满了记忆 可他却无能为力\N{\fs38}His head bursts with memories and there's nothing he can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.44,1:17:26.85,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,听一下他的音乐\N{\fs38}Listen to his music.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.28,1:17:42.11,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,看到那女的了吗?\N{\fs38}And look at that one there?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.04,1:17:47.26,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就像是想当修女的妓女\N{\fs38}She looks like a prostitute who's thinking of becoming a nun.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.45,1:17:52.60,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,真是不可思议!\N{\fs38}That's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.15,1:18:01.80,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,现在 看看这个\N{\fs38}Now, look at this one.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.93,1:18:04.98,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,看到他走路的姿势了吗?\N{\fs38}See how he walks?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.53,1:18:21.28,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,穿了别人衣服的\N{\fs38}I'd say he's in someone else's suit judging by the way he wears it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.07,1:18:31.24,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,潜入头等舱的偷渡者\N{\fs38}I'd say he's a stowaway slipped into first class
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.34,1:18:34.01,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,在寻找他的爱情之旅\N{\fs38}looking for an amorous adventure.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.11,1:18:36.79,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,美国一定是第一个映入他眼帘的\N{\fs38}This one's got America stamped on his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.85,1:18:40.30,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他一定是第一个看到的 我仿佛听到他的呐喊了\N{\fs38}He'll be the first one to see it. l can already hear him screaming.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.40,1:18:45.44,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,1900 他知道怎么阅读\N{\fs38}He knew how to read, Nineteen Hundred.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.54,1:18:48.93,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,不是读书 每个人都会读书\N{\fs38}Not books, anybody can do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.03,1:18:53.58,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他会阅人 能发现人身上的一切细节\N{\fs38}He knew how to read people, the signs people carry on them.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.58,1:18:56.37,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,地点 声音 气味\N{\fs38}Places, sounds, scents,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.37,1:19:00.30,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他们的家乡 他们的故事 身上尽显的一切\N{\fs38}their land, their story. Everything written on them.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.40,1:19:06.32,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他不但读 还把一切信息编成目录 整理后\N{\fs38}He would read, and with infinite care he would catalogue, organise,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.32,1:19:10.72,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,填入他脑海中那幅无边际的地图中去\N{\fs38}and make order in that immense map that he was drawing in his mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.82,1:19:13.34,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,也许他从未见过真实的世界\N{\fs38}Maybe he'd never seen the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.44,1:19:18.10,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但是近三十年来 世界一直向这艘船传递着各种讯息\N{\fs38}but for almost thirty years, the world had been passing on that ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.63,1:19:23.48,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,三十年来在船上的生活 他观察世界\N{\fs38}And for almost thirty years on that ship, he'd been spying on it
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.58,1:19:26.12,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,窃取世界的灵魂\N{\fs38}and he would steal its soul.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.36,1:19:36.10,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,美国!\N{\fs38}America!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.49,1:19:46.20,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我进入她的房间 她跳在我身上\N{\fs38}I went into her room, she jumped on me,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.37,1:19:49.46,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,- 我扒开她的衣服 - 继续说!\N{\fs38}- and I tore her clothes off. - Go on!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.62,1:19:52.71,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,- 你是不是总编这些啊? - 当然!\N{\fs38}- Do you always make up this crap? - Sure!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.06,1:20:59.01,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,英国辛格尔顿的李·克莱尔\N{\fs38}Singleton, Lee Claire.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.01,1:21:16.05,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,喂?\N{\fs38}Hallo?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.05,1:21:18.89,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,喂 你不认识我\N{\fs38}Hallo, you don't know me,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.89,1:21:22.24,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但我想我们可以聊聊\N{\fs38}but I was wondering if we could have a little chat.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.34,1:21:25.57,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,聊聊? 聊什么?\N{\fs38}A little chat? What about?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.67,1:21:28.02,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你想聊什么都可以... 天气情况? 你随便挑\N{\fs38}About anything you like.... Weather conditions? Anything you choose.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.12,1:21:31.02,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你来选话题\N{\fs38}Anything You pick or chuck the subject.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.08,1:21:33.37,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这是骚扰电话吗?\N{\fs38}Is this an obscene phone call?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.98,1:21:44.06,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,喂?\N{\fs38}Hallo?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.64,1:21:46.27,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,喂 这是赛马场吗?\N{\fs38}Hallo, is that the race-track?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.27,1:21:48.44,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,对 你要下注?\N{\fs38}Yeah, you betting?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.79,1:21:50.85,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,能告诉"妈妈"在比赛吗?\N{\fs38}Can you tell me if Mama's racing?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.95,1:21:52.41,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,不 是你姐姐!\N{\fs38}No, it's your sister!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.55,1:21:56.23,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我想您误会了\N{\fs38}I think there's a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.23,1:21:58.44,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,带着你的误会滚开吧!\N{\fs38}You take you misunderstanding and shove it!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.44,1:22:00.88,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,据我所知 电话能显现出人美好的一面\N{\fs38}As I known, the telephone should bring out the best in people.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.88,1:22:03.43,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你要是继续这样 我发誓会到那儿狠狠揍你一顿\N{\fs38}You keep this up, I swear I'll come over there and bring out the best in you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.43,1:22:06.23,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你真有空 你以为我不知道你是谁吗!\N{\fs38}You got still the time. You think I don't know who you are!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.39,1:22:11.31,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,天啊 他速度真快!\N{\fs38}Christ, he's already here!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.22,1:22:22.78,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,嘿 你就是那个1900?\N{\fs38}Hey, You the fish with the twenty-dollar name?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.27,1:22:39.28,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,快出来\N{\fs38}Come on out.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.84,1:22:41.03,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,见鬼!\N{\fs38}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.48,1:22:42.48,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,嘿! 你! 等会儿!\N{\fs38}Hey! You! Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.48,1:22:45.19,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,嘿! 别跑了! 只想跟你聊聊!\N{\fs38}Hey! Wait! Just want to talk to you!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.79,1:22:52.27,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,真见鬼!\N{\fs38}Holy shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.27,1:22:53.77,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我们在干什么呀 哥们?\N{\fs38}What hell are we, men?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.91,1:22:56.84,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,站住 你这狗娘养的!\N{\fs38}Hold still, you little son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.50,1:23:01.83,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,快出来!\N{\fs38}Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.84,1:23:03.25,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我们是不会伤害你的\N{\fs38}We don't want to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.25,1:23:06.86,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我们是乐手 哥们\N{\fs38}We're players, man. Sidemen.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.01,1:23:08.61,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,见鬼\N{\fs38}Damn.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.94,1:23:29.44,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,愿你好胃口!\N{\fs38}Bon appetit!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.54,1:23:32.98,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你再说一次 哥们 你再说一次\N{\fs38}You can say that again, brother. You can say that again.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.57,1:23:56.82,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你就是那个十种爵士乐元素一起演奏的人吗?\N{\fs38}You the one that plays ten kinds of jazz rolled into one?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.82,1:24:00.71,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,说实话 没数过 我只弹钢琴\N{\fs38}Tell you the truth, I've never counted them I'm just a piano player.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.71,1:24:02.02,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,是他了\N{\fs38}It's him.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.12,1:24:04.41,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,好吧 你最好现在开始数\N{\fs38}Well, you would better start counting, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.43,1:24:07.10,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,发明爵士乐的那个人派我们来找你\N{\fs38}The man who invented Jazz sent us here.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.10,1:24:10.04,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,真的? 他找我干嘛?\N{\fs38}Really? What does he want with me?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.04,1:24:13.44,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,要跟你进行钢琴决斗!\N{\fs38}He challenges you to a piano duel!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.74,1:24:16.53,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,钢琴决斗?\N{\fs38}A piano duel?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.63,1:24:19.66,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,钢琴决斗是什么?\N{\fs38}What the hell is a piano duel?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.70,1:24:23.04,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就是决斗 不过用钢琴 不是手枪\N{\fs38}It's a duel, but instead pistols of pianos.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.04,1:24:27.59,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,音乐家之间的事 不流血 只是有点仇恨\N{\fs38}It's a musicians thing. No blood, just a little hate.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.59,1:24:31.69,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,刻骨仇恨 即兴演奏你从没听过的曲子\N{\fs38}Real hate, under the skin.It riffs like you never heard.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.69,1:24:36.53,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,有时能持续一整晚 最终一方胜出\N{\fs38}It could last all night sometimes, at the end, one would win.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.41,1:24:42.48,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,1900!\N{\fs38}Nineteen Hundred!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.94,1:24:58.61,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我要是你 就不那么确定他还在这儿了\N{\fs38}If I were you, I wouldn't be so sure he's still here.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.55,1:25:03.32,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我非常了解他 他不会去别处的\N{\fs38}If I know him at all, he won't be any place else.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.68,1:25:05.40,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我非常确信\N{\fs38}I'm sure of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.50,1:25:06.82,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他走了\N{\fs38}He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.82,1:25:08.70,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,没有了钢琴 他还留这儿干什么?\N{\fs38}What would he have done here without a piano?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.72,1:25:09.76,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,一切都没了!\N{\fs38}Everything has gone!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.97,1:25:12.81,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,再说还有战争 谁知道呢?\N{\fs38}Besides, with the war, who knows?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.91,1:25:16.30,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,也许他已经不在这肮脏的人世了\N{\fs38}Maybe he's no longer part of this dirty world.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.60,1:25:20.75,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他的生命才不会如此结束的\N{\fs38}One like him doesn't end up like everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.69,1:25:23.10,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,不是他的风格\N{\fs38}It's not his style.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.10,1:25:24.31,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,随便你怎么想\N{\fs38}Think what you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.31,1:25:26.99,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但我不能因为船上有个不存在的人\N{\fs38}But I can't ask the owners to keep this carcass in the water
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.99,1:25:29.64,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,让船主留着水里的废铜烂铁\N{\fs38}just because somebody on board who doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.65,1:25:31.89,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,拖延不了很久\N{\fs38}I can't put it off much longer.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.65,1:25:38.91,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,1900 听着 我要跟你谈谈!\N{\fs38}Nineteen Hundred, listen, I have to talk to you!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.34,1:25:43.96,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,决斗怎么样了? 发生了什么?\N{\fs38}And what about the duel? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.00,1:25:47.58,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,杰里·罗尔·莫顿在1931年夏天于波士顿\N{\fs38}Jelly Roll Morton boarded the Virginian in Boston,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.65,1:25:51.18,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,登上了弗吉尼亚号\N{\fs38}Summer of 1931.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.19,1:25:53.27,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,身着一套白装\N{\fs38}Dressed entirely in white,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.28,1:25:57.23,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,手指上带着肉丸子那么大的钻石!\N{\fs38}had a diamond on his finger as size as a meatball!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.23,1:26:00.89,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,袜子上的吊带都是镶嵌着钻石\N{\fs38}Even the garters on his socks were diamond studded.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.03,1:26:11.33,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,杰里·罗尔 您为什么坐船去欧洲旅行呢?\N{\fs38}Jelly Roll, what's the reason for a trip to Europe on a steamer?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.33,1:26:14.17,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你从未坐过像密西西比河那么大的船的时候\N{\fs38}When you've never set boat that bigger than in Mississippi river.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.54,1:26:16.71,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我才不管什么欧洲!\N{\fs38}I don't give a damn about Europe!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.03,1:26:19.21,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我踏上这艘破破烂烂的船 无非就是为了\N{\fs38}The only reason why I'm hopping this crappy tub
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.31,1:26:21.74,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,与一位先生见上一面\N{\fs38}is because there's a gentleman I want to meet.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.01,1:26:25.40,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,人们说他钢琴弹得可好啦!\N{\fs38}They say he plays a hot piano!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.18,1:26:31.69,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但我倒是听说 他不敢踏上陆地\N{\fs38}But I hear he has a little thing about setting foot on land.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.78,1:26:34.60,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他是在说我吗?\N{\fs38}Is he talking about me?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.61,1:26:36.29,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你说呢 当然在说你\N{\fs38}You bet, he's talking about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.13,1:26:44.37,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他说 "嘿 杰里 有人钢琴比你弹得好"\N{\fs38}He say, "Hey, Jelly, someone plays better piano than you."
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.84,1:26:47.48,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我心里便寻思\N{\fs38}So I say to
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.58,1:26:50.49,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这家伙连从这该死的船上下来的勇气都没有\N{\fs38}self how can this cat play so well
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.59,1:26:54.52,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,怎么可能弹得一手好钢琴\N{\fs38}when he don't even have the ballsto get off the goddamn ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.62,1:26:59.93,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,嘿 见鬼了 杰里 爵士乐可是你创造的!\N{\fs38}Hey, hot damn, Jelly, you invented Jazz!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.22,1:27:04.24,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我便对自己说了:\N{\fs38}Then I says to myself:
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.34,1:27:06.55,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"你完全买得起一张一等舱的船票去欧洲\N{\fs38}"You can afford a first-class ticket to Europe
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.55,1:27:10.48,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,只要竖起一根小拇指 就能上了这艘船"\N{\fs38}and the boat that's going to take you just by lifting a finger."
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.48,1:27:13.06,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,拍一张 来 拍一张!\N{\fs38}Get a shot of it, boys, get a shot!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.06,1:27:15.36,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,说实话 你害怕吗?\N{\fs38}Tell the truth. Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.46,1:27:17.85,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs38}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.93,1:27:22.49,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,为什么要决斗? 人们决斗了会怎么样?\N{\fs38}Why a duel? What happens when you have a duel?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.49,1:27:33.23,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他看起来好像真的不怎么在乎\N{\fs38}It seemed like he really didn't care much.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.30,1:27:36.92,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就好像他根本什么都不懂 但他很好奇\N{\fs38}Like he didn't even understand it. But he was curious.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.02,1:27:40.78,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他想听听爵士乐的创造者 到底能把钢琴弹到何种境界\N{\fs38}He wanted to hear how the devil, the inventor of Jazz played.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.79,1:27:46.00,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他也没当这是玩笑 他真的相信那个人创造了爵士乐\N{\fs38}He didn't say that is a joke. He really believed that the guy invented Jazz.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.18,1:27:48.96,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我觉得 他是认为自己可以学到新东西\N{\fs38}I believe he thought he can learn something new.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.06,1:27:52.06,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他就是这样的人 和老丹尼有点像\N{\fs38}That's just how he was, a little like old Danny.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.26,1:27:53.83,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他一点竞技意识也没有\N{\fs38}He didn't have any sporting sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.83,1:27:57.90,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他才不在乎输赢 是输赢之外的事物本身最让他着迷\N{\fs38}He didn't give a damn who won, it was the rest that amazed him.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.93,1:27:59.13,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,除输赢外的一切\N{\fs38}All the rest.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.94,1:28:30.22,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,是真的!\N{\fs38}It's true!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.18,1:29:55.73,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我想 你坐了我的位置\N{\fs38}I believe you're sitting in my seat.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:07.16,1:30:09.47,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你就是创造爵士乐的那位 对吧?\N{\fs38}You're the one who invented Jazz, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.49,1:30:11.69,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,人们是这么说的\N{\fs38}That's what they say.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.82,1:30:20.06,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你就是人不在海上 就弹不好琴的那位 对吧?\N{\fs38}And you're the one who can't play unless you have the ocean under your ass? Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.07,1:30:21.99,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我是这么说的\N{\fs38}That's what I say.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.48,1:30:34.68,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,劳驾 请让一下!\N{\fs38}Excusez-moi, s'il vous plait!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.76,1:31:27.62,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,杰里·罗尔·莫顿不是在演奏 而是轻抚着乐符\N{\fs38}Jelly Roll Morton did not play,he caressed those notes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.68,1:31:31.48,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就好像真丝轻轻滑下女人的胴体\N{\fs38}It sounded like a silk slipsliding down a woman's body.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.58,1:31:34.96,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他的双手如蝴蝶般轻盈\N{\fs38}His hands were butterflies, so light.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.44,1:31:39.28,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他起步于新奥尔良有名的油水区\N{\fs38}He got his start in the famed tenderloin districts of New Orleans,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.29,1:31:43.39,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,而他却是在仓库里学会弹琴的\N{\fs38}and all did he learn to stroke the keyboard in those whorehouses.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.42,1:31:46.94,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,楼上干活的人们都不出大声\N{\fs38}People doing the deed upstairs didn't want any uproar.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:46.94,1:31:51.40,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他们想要音乐滑过窗帘 藏在床下\N{\fs38}They wanted music that would slipbehind the curtains, under the beds,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.49,1:31:56.05,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,柔情中却不缺澎湃 他弹的音乐就是这样\N{\fs38}without disturbing the passion. That's the kind of music he played.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.05,1:32:00.50,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,如此说来 他的确无人可比\N{\fs38}And in that, he truly was the best.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.16,1:33:03.29,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,- 棒! - 棒!\N{\fs38}- Bravo! - Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.90,1:33:36.19,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,该你了 水手小子\N{\fs38}Your turn, sailor.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.86,1:33:52.11,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,加油\N{\fs38}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.20,1:34:30.04,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他弹的这是什么呀?\N{\fs38}What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.65,1:34:37.82,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"平安夜"?\N{\fs38}"Silent Night"?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.82,1:34:39.88,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这不是圣诞颂歌吗?\N{\fs38}Isn't that a Christmas carol?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.88,1:34:42.28,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他知道这是在比赛吗?\N{\fs38}Does he understand it's a contest?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.38,1:34:44.52,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"平安夜"也算爵士乐?\N{\fs38}"Silenet Night" is Jazz?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.82,1:34:47.18,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,原来到圣诞节啦?\N{\fs38}Is it Christmas already?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.96,1:35:12.94,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他赢了吗 先生?\N{\fs38}Did he win, signor?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.94,1:35:14.82,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,不 这才刚开始\N{\fs38}No, they're just warming up.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.82,1:35:16.03,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,太棒了!\N{\fs38}Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.20,1:35:21.28,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,来吧 杰里·罗尔 让我们见识见识真正的爵士乐!\N{\fs38}Come on, Jelly Roll, show us what Jazz is all about!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.14,1:36:17.84,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你脑子进水了吗?\N{\fs38}What is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.33,1:36:22.13,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我情不自禁 这音乐弄得我想哭\N{\fs38}I can't help it. Music makes me cry.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.13,1:36:24.07,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,每一个船员都押了你!\N{\fs38}The whole crew bet on you!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.07,1:36:27.80,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我把一年的薪水都押进去了! 你却在这哭哭啼啼的?\N{\fs38}I put a year's pay on the line! And you're crying?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.80,1:36:30.78,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,别扯淡了 赶紧琢磨你的音乐吧!\N{\fs38}Now you cut that out and start thinking your music!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.98,1:36:32.07,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我也能押吗?\N{\fs38}Can I bet, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.07,1:36:36.14,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,不行! 自己押自己不吉利\N{\fs38}No! It's bad luck to bet on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.14,1:36:39.02,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我不想押自己 我想押他 他弹得太好了\N{\fs38}I don't want to bet on me. I want to bet on him. He's the greatest.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.22,1:36:43.19,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你这人疯了 你知道吗?\N{\fs38}You are crazy, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.19,1:36:45.72,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那样的话 你要是赌输了 我还能帮你把钱赢回来\N{\fs38}That way, if you lose I'll get your money back.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.26,1:37:49.97,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,亲爱的 跟刚刚完全是同一首曲子\N{\fs38}It's exactly the same piece of music, darling.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.24,1:37:53.98,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,当然 也没什么不可以 毕竟是比赛\N{\fs38}Yeah, sure, it's OK. But this is a competition.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.93,1:37:58.24,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这实在是有点过分了\N{\fs38}This is really the end of the line.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.47,1:38:03.22,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,不敢相信\N{\fs38}Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.63,1:39:07.05,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他输了吗 先生?\N{\fs38}Did he lose, signor?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.05,1:39:08.48,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,还没\N{\fs38}Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.90,1:39:12.83,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,棒!\N{\fs38}Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.65,1:39:22.84,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你这是自取其辱!\N{\fs38}You stick this up your ass!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.08,1:40:21.50,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,嘿 马克斯?\N{\fs38}Hey, Max?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.73,1:40:24.06,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,能给我支香烟吗?\N{\fs38}Give me a cigarette, will you?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.06,1:40:26.54,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你真是瞎胡闹\N{\fs38}You're not handling this well.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.59,1:40:27.98,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,给我支香烟\N{\fs38}Just give me a cigarette.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.99,1:40:29.69,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你根本都不抽烟\N{\fs38}You don't smoke.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.01,1:40:34.65,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你脑子有问题吗? 你单手都能甩他十条街!\N{\fs38}What is the matter with you? You could lick this guy with one hand!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:34.94,1:40:36.31,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,真是的!\N{\fs38}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.48,1:41:02.15,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我没听清\N{\fs38}Pardon me, I didn't catch that.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.15,1:41:04.08,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我还什么都没说呢 先生\N{\fs38}I didn't say anything, signor.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.07,1:41:07.05,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,棒!\N{\fs38}Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.99,1:41:11.30,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你到底给不给一支香烟?\N{\fs38}Are you going to give me a cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.30,1:41:14.99,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,咱们接下来得铲八辈子煤了 你却满嘴...\N{\fs38}We'll be chucking coal a couple hundred years, and all you can say is...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.99,1:41:17.12,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他妈的快拿支香烟给我 听见没?\N{\fs38}Give me a fucking cigarette, will you?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.17,1:41:24.63,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,跳梁小丑!\N{\fs38}Clown!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.83,1:41:51.95,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这是你自找的 混蛋\N{\fs38}You asked for it, asshole.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.32,1:45:07.65,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你来抽吧 我不会吸烟\N{\fs38}You smoke it. I don't know how.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.83,1:45:15.41,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮! 棒!\N{\fs38}Well done! Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.46,1:45:21.46,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你是最棒的!\N{\fs38}You're the greatest!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.67,1:45:23.92,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,神了!\N{\fs38}Divine!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.33,1:45:35.37,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他赢了吗 先生?\N{\fs38}Did he win, signor?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.38,1:45:37.38,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,是的 他赢了\N{\fs38}Yes, he won.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.85,1:45:39.76,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我就知道他会赢 先生!\N{\fs38}I knew he would, signor!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.74,1:46:28.11,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,杰里·罗尔·莫顿接下来一路都把自己锁在屋内\N{\fs38}Jelly Roll Morton spend the rest of that trip locked in his cabin.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.40,1:46:33.54,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,到达南安普敦之后 他下了维吉尼亚号 回到美国\N{\fs38}When we got to Southampton, he got off the Virginian and went back to America.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.45,1:46:39.15,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我记得1900看着他走到码头\N{\fs38}I remember Nineteen Hundred watched him as he walked off down the dock.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.33,1:46:41.06,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,只说了一句\N{\fs38}And all he said
Dialogue: 0,1:46:41.06,1:46:43.18,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,去他的爵士乐!\N{\fs38}Fuck Jazz, too!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.05,1:46:50.53,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他就是这么说的 "去他的爵士乐!"\N{\fs38}That's just what he said: "Fuck Jazz, too!"
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.53,1:46:53.13,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,真是很不可思议的故事\N{\fs38}This is an incredible story.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.13,1:46:54.64,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我漏听了什么重要情节吗?\N{\fs38}Did I miss anything important?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.65,1:46:55.94,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,可以这么说\N{\fs38}You could say that.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.94,1:46:57.01,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,该死!\N{\fs38}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.01,1:47:00.29,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,别担心 这位朋友之后会再跟你讲一遍的 对吧?\N{\fs38}Don't worry, our friend will fill you in later. Won't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.29,1:47:01.42,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,包在我身上\N{\fs38}You can count on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.43,1:47:02.50,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,谢谢了\N{\fs38}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.50,1:47:04.85,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他真是很会讲故事\N{\fs38}He's really good at telling tales.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:05.75,1:47:08.04,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这不是什么故事 先生\N{\fs38}This is no tale, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.86,1:47:15.49,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,没错 我这一生干了很多蠢事\N{\fs38}Yeah, I've done lots of stupid things in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:15.70,1:47:19.51,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我已经可悲到一无所有的地步了\N{\fs38}If you were to hang me upside down nothing would fall out my pockets.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.80,1:47:22.82,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我连自己的小号都卖了 什么都不剩了!\N{\fs38}I even sold my trumpet. Everything!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.13,1:47:26.73,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但唯独这个故事 我至今珍藏\N{\fs38}But not this story, I haven't lost that.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.92,1:47:30.93,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我现在把这个故事讲出来 仅仅是为了救他\N{\fs38}Now, I've decided to tell it only because I want to save him.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.00,1:47:34.12,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但这里没有人 一个人都没有! 听得懂吗?\N{\fs38}But there's no-one here. Nobody! Understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.51,1:47:37.00,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那是因为我们人太多 吓到他了\N{\fs38}It's because there are too many of us, we've scared him.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.00,1:47:40.70,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,对不起 但要么你现在就给我下船 不然就叫人逮捕你\N{\fs38}I'm sorry. Now, you leave this ship or I'll have to have you arrested.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.65,1:47:43.40,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,回去干活 别磨蹭!\N{\fs38}Get back to work. Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.10,1:47:46.30,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,再给我一个机会吧\N{\fs38}Give me another chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.30,1:47:47.54,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,滚吧 朋友\N{\fs38}Piss off, friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.55,1:47:49.94,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,明天中午 这船就是历史了!\N{\fs38}Noon tomorrow this ship is history!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.50,1:48:05.67,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但是...\N{\fs38}And yet....
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.79,1:48:07.95,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,找到了\N{\fs38}Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.62,1:48:10.09,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,住手 不然我开枪了!\N{\fs38}Stop or I'll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.44,1:48:12.75,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,抓到你了\N{\fs38}Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.85,1:48:15.39,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,老爷子 冷静 是我\N{\fs38}Pops, easy, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:19.53,1:48:21.07,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,又是你 对吧?\N{\fs38}You again? Is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.17,1:48:23.43,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,嗯 把枪放下 好吗?\N{\fs38}Yes, lower that cannon, will you?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.44,1:48:27.74,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,卖出自己的乐器再偷回去 老花头了!\N{\fs38}Sell your instrument and then steal it back, that's an old trick!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.84,1:48:29.75,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我早该知道你是个贼\N{\fs38}I should have known you're a thief.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.75,1:48:32.13,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,不 我是在找这个\N{\fs38}No, I was looking for this.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.13,1:48:33.33,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你要它干什么?\N{\fs38}And what do you need that for?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.72,1:48:35.61,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这关乎生死啊\N{\fs38}It's a matter of life and death.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.61,1:48:37.22,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我还需要一台唱机\N{\fs38}And I need a phonograph, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.24,1:48:38.80,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,又偷东西还撒谎\N{\fs38}A thief and a liar.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.90,1:48:41.03,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,听我说! 老爷子 我没多少时间了\N{\fs38}Look! Pops, I don't have a whole lot of time here.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.05,1:48:43.54,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我倒是闲得很 毕竟拿枪的是我\N{\fs38}Well, I do! Seeing as I have a gun.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:44.19,1:48:48.97,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这下我倒想起来了 什么时候蒸汽船上可以做唱片了?\N{\fs38}And now that I think of it, since when were records made on board steamships?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.03,1:48:51.79,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,冒牌货!\N{\fs38}Impostor!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.35,1:48:54.30,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,要是这音乐真的出自你朋友之手\N{\fs38}If that music really was played by your friend,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.30,1:48:57.29,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那就意味着 他一生中 至少有一次 下过那艘船!\N{\fs38}it means that at some time in his life he got off that ship!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:57.49,1:48:58.70,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,对不对?\N{\fs38}Correct?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.73,1:49:00.29,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,不可能 老大爷\N{\fs38}Not a chance, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:00.44,1:49:03.47,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他亲自录制了这张充满激情的唱片\N{\fs38}He cut this passionate recording personally.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:03.48,1:49:05.51,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我认为这是他的巅峰之作!\N{\fs38}I think it's his best work!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.52,1:49:09.92,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但他一秒钟都没下过那艘船\N{\fs38}But he didn't jump ship to do it, not even for a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:09.93,1:49:15.25,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这是唱片制造史上一次绝无仅有的经历\N{\fs38}It was an extraordinary, unique event in the history of record-making.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.25,1:49:18.30,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,1900先生 人没有极限\N{\fs38}The sky's the limit, Mr. Nineteen Hundred.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.30,1:49:22.10,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,如果 而且我们觉得这张唱片一定会大卖特卖\N{\fs38}If this record sells like hotcakes and we think it will,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.11,1:49:24.51,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你能走得很远 十九先生\N{\fs38}You'll go far, Mr. Nineteen.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.71,1:49:27.47,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,您介意我叫您十九吗?\N{\fs38}Do you mind if I call you Nineteen?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.57,1:49:29.17,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这个会不会痛啊?\N{\fs38}This is going to hurt, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.21,1:49:32.39,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,准备好了 先生们 数到三\N{\fs38}Ready now, gentelmen. On the count.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:32.49,1:49:35.88,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,一 二 三\N{\fs38}And one, two, three.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.24,1:52:35.18,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,噢 十九!\N{\fs38}Oh, Nineteen!
Dialogue: 0,1:52:35.21,1:52:40.58,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,真是绝了 这曲子叫什么名字?\N{\fs38}That is one amazing piece of music. What is it called?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:41.48,1:52:45.06,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,肯定能让人们感动得嚎啕大哭\N{\fs38}It's going to have people crying buckets.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:45.16,1:52:48.61,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,不过得起个合适的名字 朗朗上口的...\N{\fs38}It's got to have the right title though, something catchy like....
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.62,1:52:51.09,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"风中摇摆"或者...\N{\fs38}"Swinging in the Breeze" or...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:51.46,1:52:53.85,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,天籁 一如既往\N{\fs38}Great, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:53.85,1:52:55.45,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"甜蜜十九" 就这个...\N{\fs38}"Sweet Nineteen," that's it...
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.55,1:52:57.83,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你肯定会出大名\N{\fs38}You're going to be big time.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.84,1:53:00.66,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你只需要迈出那伟大的一步\N{\fs38}And all you got to do is take that big step.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.07,1:53:06.52,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,什么伟大的一步?\N{\fs38}What big step?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.53,1:53:08.06,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,下船啊\N{\fs38}Getting off.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:08.16,1:53:12.38,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,离开这堆破破烂烂的木头 去追寻...\N{\fs38}Getting off these lousy planks of wood and going after...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:13.00,1:53:16.60,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,追寻属于你的名望和财富\N{\fs38}Going after your fame and fortune.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.69,1:53:20.26,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我不是有意插嘴 但...\N{\fs38}I don't mean to butt in fellas, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.27,1:53:27.90,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你就算再也不下船 这张唱片也足够养活你一辈子了\N{\fs38}with this, you can have anything you want and never have to set foot off this boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:44.47,1:53:48.27,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我们将这张唱片复制几百万份\N{\fs38}We'll print millions of copies,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.35,1:53:53.93,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这样全世界的人都能聆听到你的美妙音乐 十九\N{\fs38}so that people all over the world can hear your wonderful music, Nineteen.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:55.52,1:53:57.35,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,十九先生?\N{\fs38}Mr. Nineteen?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:57.46,1:54:00.47,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,没有我 我的音乐哪儿也不能去\N{\fs38}I won't let my music go anywhere without me.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:03.30,1:54:04.99,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,不! 别碰\N{\fs38}No! Don't touch.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:04.99,1:54:06.73,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你在干什么? 你不能这么做\N{\fs38}What are you doing? You can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.83,1:54:09.59,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我们签过合同的 你现在不能反悔啊\N{\fs38}We have a contract. You can't go back now.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:10.37,1:54:12.04,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我一向反悔的\N{\fs38}I always go back.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:15.72,1:55:17.52,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,小姐\N{\fs38}Miss,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:20.21,1:55:24.72,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,要是你... 会是我的荣幸\N{\fs38}I'd be pleased if you...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:36.21,1:55:40.42,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,小姐 我很高兴...\N{\fs38}Miss, I'd be...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:42.29,1:55:44.50,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我很激动...\N{\fs38}I'd be thrilled...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.05,1:55:49.51,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,要是你能收下这份...\N{\fs38}if you'd accept this...
Dialogue: 0,1:55:51.59,1:55:54.85,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,小小的心意...\N{\fs38}small token...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:11.59,1:57:15.68,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,嗨 帕多安小姐 您一个人在这儿干什么呢? 在数海浪吗?\N{\fs38}Hey, Miss Padoan, what are you doing here all alone? Counting the waves?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:15.75,1:57:18.87,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,船长说我们马上就要穿过北回归线了\N{\fs38}The captain said we'd be passing the Tropic of Cancer soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:18.88,1:57:21.43,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,太棒了! 至少有东西可看了\N{\fs38}Great! At least we'll have something to look at.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:21.60,1:57:25.17,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你注意到海水是怎么改变颜色的吗? 一天十次\N{\fs38}You ever notice how the sea changes colors? Ten times a day.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:25.20,1:57:29.37,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,甚至更多 我愿意整天盯着海看\N{\fs38}Even more. I could look at the sea all day long.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:29.37,1:57:31.35,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,要知道 农民是不看海的啊\N{\fs38}You know farmers don't ever look at the sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:31.35,1:57:34.06,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他们害怕海 至少我是这么听说的\N{\fs38}It scares them. At least that's what I heard.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:34.16,1:57:35.91,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,不是这样的\N{\fs38}That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:36.76,1:57:41.06,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,有次 我父亲跟我说他听到了海的声音\N{\fs38}Once, my father told me he heard the ocean's voice.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:41.37,1:57:43.84,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,真的? 海说了什么?\N{\fs38}Really? What did it say?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:44.95,1:57:48.12,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,不能告诉你 这是秘密\N{\fs38}I can't tell you. It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:48.52,1:57:50.46,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,秘密就应该保守\N{\fs38}And secrets should be kept.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:50.49,1:57:53.81,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,天啊 雨彻底下大了 快进去吧\N{\fs38}Gosh, it's really coming down now. Let's get back inside.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:53.81,1:57:55.06,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,走吧!\N{\fs38}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:55.68,1:57:57.17,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我扶着您\N{\fs38}Let me take your arm.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:56.71,1:58:59.06,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"三等舱 女寝"\N{\fs38}"Women's dormitory 3 class"
Dialogue: 0,2:03:01.17,2:03:03.17,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,美国!\N{\fs38}America!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:03.41,2:03:07.56,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,该死的 明明应该是我先喊的!\N{\fs38}Damn it, I wanted to say it!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:36.72,2:03:38.90,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,劳驾\N{\fs38}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:39.97,2:03:41.39,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,劳驾\N{\fs38}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:43.12,2:03:44.62,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fs38}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:46.49,2:03:48.04,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,小姐 请留步\N{\fs38}Please, miss.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:51.40,2:03:53.06,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我得和你说句话\N{\fs38}I have to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:59.67,2:04:02.02,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你是要去和你父亲见面 对吗?\N{\fs38}You're meeting your father, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:02.30,2:04:03.77,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs38}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:04.55,2:04:05.74,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道的?\N{\fs38}How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:05.76,2:04:07.66,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我想我见过他\N{\fs38}I think I've met him.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:11.58,2:04:15.75,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就在这艘船上 好些年前了\N{\fs38}On this ship, quite a few years ago.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:16.10,2:04:18.51,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我不确定他搭的是否就是这艘船\N{\fs38}I don't know if he took this same ship.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:19.07,2:04:22.36,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我肯定\N{\fs38}I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:23.96,2:04:27.01,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他有一支缪塞特笛 对吗?\N{\fs38}He has a musette. Yes?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:28.73,2:04:30.74,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我们还一起演奏来着\N{\fs38}I think we played together.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:32.00,2:04:36.63,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我也不确定他还记不记得我了 但... 代我向他问好\N{\fs38}I don't know if he'd remember, but... say hello to him.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:38.01,2:04:41.08,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,好 我会的\N{\fs38}All right, I will.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:41.15,2:04:45.53,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但你怎么知道我是谁? 这很奇怪 不是吗?\N{\fs38}But how did you know who I was? It's very strange, no?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:45.64,2:04:47.64,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这是秘密\N{\fs38}It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:49.03,2:04:51.91,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,秘密就应该保守\N{\fs38}And secrets should be kept.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:51.98,2:04:54.59,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,尽管我觉得你父亲当时好像不是这么想的\N{\fs38}Although I think your father felt differently back then.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:56.07,2:05:00.15,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,走吧! 快往前走! 不然咱们得在这儿困一个礼拜了\N{\fs38}Come on! Keep moving! Or we'll be here all week to discipline!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:19.58,2:05:23.41,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,请收下这份... 小小的心意\N{\fs38}Please accept this... small musical token.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:23.46,2:05:26.34,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,对不起 我听不见你\N{\fs38}I'm sorry, but I can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:27.34,2:05:33.75,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我想请你... 收下这份小小的心意\N{\fs38}I want you to... accept this small token.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:34.51,2:05:36.30,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我听不见你\N{\fs38}I can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:41.55,2:05:42.89,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,祝你好运\N{\fs38}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:42.99,2:05:45.67,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 也祝你好运\N{\fs38}Thank you. Good luck to you, too.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:47.12,2:05:49.79,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,以后有空来我们家玩呗?\N{\fs38}Why don't you come and visit us some day?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:49.79,2:05:52.98,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我们住在莫特街27号\N{\fs38}We live on Mott Street. Number 27.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:52.98,2:05:55.14,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我父亲是卖鱼的\N{\fs38}My father has a fish shop.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:56.17,2:05:57.81,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,可能吧...\N{\fs38}Maybe....
Dialogue: 0,2:06:05.20,2:06:08.62,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,帕多安 好 下一个\N{\fs38}Padoan, okay. Next.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:08.69,2:06:10.22,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,下一个\N{\fs38}Next.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:52.46,2:06:56.41,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他再也没向我提过她 我也没再问过\N{\fs38}He never mentioned her to me again,and I never asked.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:56.45,2:06:59.46,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,至少接下来十二个来回都没提过\N{\fs38}At least not for the next twelve crossings.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:00.55,2:07:03.60,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,再说了 他还一如既往地乐呵\N{\fs38}Besides, he was happy just like always.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:03.81,2:07:06.02,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那是他最受欢迎的一段时间\N{\fs38}His popularity was at its peak.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:06.78,2:07:12.95,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我们都无法想象 在他看似兴高采烈的外表下 内心是怎样的波澜\N{\fs38}None of us could have imagined what was smoldering beneath the ashes of his apparent happiness.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:13.86,2:07:18.67,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,之后 春天的一个夜晚 热内亚到纽约半途\N{\fs38}Then, one evening in spring, halfway between Genoa and New York,
Dialogue: 0,2:07:18.68,2:07:20.89,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就在大洋正中间\N{\fs38}right in the middle of the ocean,
Dialogue: 0,2:07:20.90,2:07:22.77,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,油画掉了下来\N{\fs38}the painting fell.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:22.80,2:07:25.62,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,什么意思? 什么叫油画掉了下来?\N{\fs38}What do you meaning? The painting fell?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:25.73,2:07:29.34,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,老大爷 你有没有想过 为什么油画会掉下来?\N{\fs38}Pops, have you ever asked yourself why paintings fall?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:29.35,2:07:30.21,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,没想过\N{\fs38}No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:30.21,2:07:33.31,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我一直对油画这点很着迷\N{\fs38}I've always been impressed by this thing about paintings.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:33.31,2:07:34.97,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,油画跟这故事有什么关系?\N{\fs38}What's the painting got to do with this ?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:34.97,2:07:36.07,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,有关系\N{\fs38}It does.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:36.08,2:07:40.24,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,因为对1900来说 那晚就和油画掉落一样\N{\fs38}Because for Nineteen Hundred, that night went the way it does for paintings.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:40.81,2:07:46.09,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,油画在那安安稳稳挂了许多年 但毫无征兆...\N{\fs38}They hang there for years, and then without any happening...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:46.09,2:07:47.56,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,一点征兆也没有...\N{\fs38}Nothing at all...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:49.55,2:07:51.02,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就掉了下来\N{\fs38}Down that come.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:51.54,2:07:54.64,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就这么挂在钉子上 都没人碰它\N{\fs38}They're hanging there on that nail, no-body even touches them,
Dialogue: 0,2:07:54.64,2:07:56.62,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但到某一时间...\N{\fs38}But at a certain point...
Dialogue: 0,2:07:58.28,2:08:04.24,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就这么义无反顾 不声不响地掉了下来\N{\fs38}they fall down anyway, in the most absolute silence.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:04.44,2:08:09.26,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,周围的事物完好如初\N{\fs38}With everything perfectly still around them.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:10.26,2:08:14.06,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,连苍蝇都不曾飞过\N{\fs38}Not even a fly moving.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:14.44,2:08:16.66,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,而它们...\N{\fs38}And they...
Dialogue: 0,2:08:19.81,2:08:24.56,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,一点原因也没有 为什么这么突然呢?\N{\fs38}There's no reason. Why in that instant?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:25.10,2:08:26.73,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,谁知道呢?\N{\fs38}Who knows ?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:31.06,2:08:34.70,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,钉子到底遭遇了什么\N{\fs38}What happens to a nail
Dialogue: 0,2:08:34.70,2:08:41.50,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,让它认为自己再也承受不住了呢?\N{\fs38}to make it decide that it just can't anymore?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:43.05,2:08:46.46,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那可怜的小家伙也有灵魂吗?\N{\fs38}Does he have a soul, too, poor thing?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:46.69,2:08:48.77,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,它也会做决定?\N{\fs38}Does he make decisions ?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:48.87,2:08:50.59,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,坐下来...\N{\fs38}Sit down...
Dialogue: 0,2:08:51.35,2:08:54.39,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,莫非钉子和油画经过了长时间的讨论?\N{\fs38}Did the nail discuss this at length with the painting?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:54.39,2:08:56.11,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他们拿不准该不该这么做\N{\fs38}They were unsure about doing it.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:56.12,2:08:58.53,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,于是多年来每晚都讨论一番?\N{\fs38}They talked it over every night for years ?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:58.53,2:09:04.49,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,然后他们便决定在那一天 那一分 那一秒 那么一瞬间?\N{\fs38}And then they decide on a date, a time, a minute, a precise instant?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:05.52,2:09:10.86,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,还是说他们一开始就知悉? 它们俩都命中注定?\N{\fs38}Or they both know it from the beginning? Both of them was already set up?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:11.13,2:09:14.48,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"听着! 我七年以后就放手"\N{\fs38}"Look! I'm letting go in seven years."
Dialogue: 0,2:09:14.48,2:09:15.75,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"我同意"\N{\fs38}"Fine with me."
Dialogue: 0,2:09:15.85,2:09:18.20,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"那说好了 五月十三日"\N{\fs38}"So understand, on May 13."
Dialogue: 0,2:09:18.20,2:09:19.12,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"好"\N{\fs38}"Okay."
Dialogue: 0,2:09:19.12,2:09:20.16,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"十二点整?"\N{\fs38}"At twelve o'clock?"
Dialogue: 0,2:09:20.16,2:09:21.84,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"十二点一刻如何?"\N{\fs38}"How about twelve fifteen?"
Dialogue: 0,2:09:21.84,2:09:22.98,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"没问题"\N{\fs38}"OK."
Dialogue: 0,2:09:22.98,2:09:24.75,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"那晚安了"\N{\fs38}"So good night."
Dialogue: 0,2:09:25.63,2:09:28.64,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,七年之后 五月十三日这天\N{\fs38}Seven years later, on May 13,
Dialogue: 0,2:09:28.65,2:09:31.09,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,十二点一刻...\N{\fs38}at twelve fifteen...
Dialogue: 0,2:09:35.20,2:09:37.09,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,根本无法理解\N{\fs38}It's impossible to understand.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:37.09,2:09:39.68,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这种事情或许还是不要去想的好!\N{\fs38}It's one of those things that probably better not to think about!
Dialogue: 0,2:09:39.69,2:09:41.21,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,因为想下去会发疯的\N{\fs38}Because it makes you nuts.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:41.51,2:09:42.94,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,一切都很突然\N{\fs38}Paintings fall,
Dialogue: 0,2:09:43.56,2:09:46.84,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就像画掉了下来 就像你一早醒来 发现那个她不再爱你\N{\fs38}when you wake up one morningand discover she doesn't love you anymore,
Dialogue: 0,2:09:47.15,2:09:50.70,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就像你打开报纸 看到战争爆发的消息\N{\fs38}when you open a newspaperand read that war has broken out,
Dialogue: 0,2:09:50.70,2:09:54.13,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就像你看见列车 就想到我将离开此地\N{\fs38}when you see a train and you think I got to leave this place,
Dialogue: 0,2:09:54.13,2:09:56.49,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,当看到镜子里自己 你想自己老了\N{\fs38}when you look in a mirrorand realise you're old.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:56.97,2:09:59.63,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,有一天晚上 在茫茫的大海上\N{\fs38}When one evening, in the middle of the ocean,
Dialogue: 0,2:09:59.73,2:10:07.44,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,1900把视线移开他的餐盘 双目凝视着我说...\N{\fs38}Nineteen Hundred looks up from his plate,looks me in the eyes and...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:07.69,2:10:10.14,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,三天后这船就到纽约 到时候我就下船\N{\fs38}In three days when we get to New York, I'm getting off this ship.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:13.61,2:10:17.52,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我实在是太惊讶了\N{\fs38}I was flabbergasted.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:19.59,2:10:21.59,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,无语了?\N{\fs38}Cat got your tongue?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:23.37,2:10:27.13,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,不 我为你高兴\N{\fs38}No,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:27.78,2:10:29.86,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但是不是太突然了?\N{\fs38}But all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:31.28,2:10:32.57,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,是有点突然\N{\fs38}All of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:34.80,2:10:37.07,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,老兄...\N{\fs38}My man...
Dialogue: 0,2:10:37.40,2:10:38.67,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,太棒啦\N{\fs38}that's aces.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:38.67,2:10:40.68,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我想下船见识一些东西\N{\fs38}I've got to see something down there.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:40.88,2:10:42.01,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,什么?\N{\fs38}What?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:42.01,2:10:43.52,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,大海\N{\fs38}The ocean.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:46.25,2:10:47.54,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,大海?\N{\fs38}The ocean?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:47.60,2:10:48.96,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,嗯 大海\N{\fs38}The ocean.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:54.33,2:10:55.93,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你不会逗我玩吧?\N{\fs38}You're pulling my leg?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:56.45,2:10:59.55,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你从一出生就一直在看着大海\N{\fs38}You've seen nothing but the ocean since the day you were born.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:59.55,2:11:00.76,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但是从船上看的\N{\fs38}But from here.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:02.66,2:11:05.53,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我想从陆地上看 应该会完全不一样\N{\fs38}I want to see it from there. It's not the same thing at all.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:05.92,2:11:08.83,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那就等到靠岸了 靠着船边看呗\N{\fs38}Wait till we dock, lean over the side, take a good look.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:08.83,2:11:10.37,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,不都一样嘛\N{\fs38}It's the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:10.92,2:11:12.13,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,不 不一样\N{\fs38}No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:13.26,2:11:15.41,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,从陆地上看 你能听到海的声音\N{\fs38}From land, you can hear its voice.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:15.51,2:11:17.69,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,在船上是听不到这种声音的\N{\fs38}You don't hear that from a ship.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:18.66,2:11:21.24,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,大海的声音? 那是什么?\N{\fs38}What do you mean, its voice?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:21.30,2:11:22.90,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,它的声音\N{\fs38}Its voice.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:26.86,2:11:32.61,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就像是... 呐喊...\N{\fs38}It's like... a big scream...
Dialogue: 0,2:11:34.34,2:11:38.11,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,告诉你生活是有无限可能的\N{\fs38}telling you that life is immense.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:38.64,2:11:40.07,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,只要听见了大海的声音\N{\fs38}Once you've finally heard it,
Dialogue: 0,2:11:40.07,2:11:43.47,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那样你就知道了你以后的人生目标\N{\fs38}then you really know what you have to do to go on living.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:44.32,2:11:46.76,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我可以选择一直呆在船上\N{\fs38}I could stay here forever,
Dialogue: 0,2:11:47.98,2:11:52.54,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但大海从来不对我诉说什么\N{\fs38}but the ocean would never tell me a thing.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:53.26,2:11:57.46,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但也许我下了船 在陆地上生活几年\N{\fs38}But if I get off, live on land for a couple of years,
Dialogue: 0,2:11:57.46,2:12:01.81,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,也许我就会变得像别人一样正常\N{\fs38}then I'll be normal. Just like the others.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:02.38,2:12:06.04,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,然后某天 我再去海边\N{\fs38}Then maybe one day, I'll make it to the coast,
Dialogue: 0,2:12:06.12,2:12:10.64,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,抬头远望大海 也许就能听见大海对我的呐喊了\N{\fs38}look up, see the ocean, and hear it scream.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:13.65,2:12:16.16,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我不知道你是听谁瞎扯的\N{\fs38}I don't know who's been telling you all thisbullshit
Dialogue: 0,2:12:16.16,2:12:18.46,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,或是你自己编的\N{\fs38}or if you're just making it up.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:18.71,2:12:20.91,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你知道我怎么看吗?\N{\fs38}But you want to know what I think?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:21.81,2:12:23.45,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我觉得...\N{\fs38}I think...
Dialogue: 0,2:12:24.00,2:12:28.97,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你想下船的原因是那个女孩\N{\fs38}the real reason you want off this ship is the girl.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:29.48,2:12:31.65,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,英雄难过美人关\N{\fs38}It's always the girl.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:31.75,2:12:35.99,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,即使不是因为这个 我也支持你\N{\fs38}But even if it's not the reason, that suits me just fine.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:36.61,2:12:41.81,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,因为我也想让你下船 给岸上的人弹奏音乐\N{\fs38}Because I've always wanted you to leave this ship and play for the people on land.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:41.91,2:12:45.38,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,然后结婚生子\N{\fs38}And marry a nice woman and have children,
Dialogue: 0,2:12:45.48,2:12:50.71,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,虽然这一切并不是像你所说 具有无限可能\N{\fs38}and all those things in life which are not immense
Dialogue: 0,2:12:51.59,2:12:53.91,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但是值得为之努力\N{\fs38}but are worth the effort.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:55.80,2:12:59.57,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你会过来看我的 对吧? 在岸上?\N{\fs38}You'll come visit me, won't you, Max? On land?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:03.46,2:13:05.49,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fs38}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:07.40,2:13:11.14,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,想象一下 你会让我认识你孩子的母亲\N{\fs38}That way, you'll introduce meto the mother of your children,
Dialogue: 0,2:13:12.43,2:13:15.13,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,邀请我周末去你家吃饭\N{\fs38}and invite me for Sunday dinner.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:15.58,2:13:18.44,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我会带一些甜点和一瓶红酒\N{\fs38}I'll bring the dessert and a bottle of wine
Dialogue: 0,2:13:18.44,2:13:21.47,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,然后你会说 太客气了 本不用带东西的\N{\fs38}and you'll tell me I shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:21.94,2:13:27.68,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,然后你会带我参观你的家 那外形就像一条船\N{\fs38}And while you're showing me around your house shaped like a ship,
Dialogue: 0,2:13:28.33,2:13:33.97,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你的妻子正在做火鸡 然后我们一起坐在餐桌前\N{\fs38}your wife will be cooking a turkey. And then we'll sit at the table.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:34.04,2:13:37.86,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我会夸你老婆是个好厨子\N{\fs38}I'll tell her she's an excellent cook,
Dialogue: 0,2:13:37.96,2:13:41.66,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,然后她会说 你老是说我过去如何如何\N{\fs38}and she'll say how you talk about me all the time.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:45.59,2:13:49.86,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我要把我的驼绒大衣送给你\N{\fs38}You know, I'm going to give you my camel coat.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:50.44,2:13:53.69,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你穿着那件大衣下船时 看上去会很精神\N{\fs38}You'll cut a fine figure when you get down there.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:57.68,2:14:00.28,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你觉得我如果有匹马 还能不能结婚呀?\N{\fs38}You think I could have a family with a horse?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:11.92,2:14:13.16,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,- 1900! - 嘿!\N{\fs38}- Nineteen Hundred! - Hey!
Dialogue: 0,2:14:13.16,2:14:18.30,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我见过很多人下船时的离别 很多都是虚情假意的\N{\fs38}How many people I have seen saying goodbye on the docks without giving a damn.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:19.06,2:14:23.89,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但我和1900告别的时候 却有一种真心的失落感\N{\fs38}But when I said goodbye to Nineteen Hundred, it was a real blow.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:56.48,2:14:58.69,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,在外当心点 好吗?\N{\fs38}Be careful, all right?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:09.57,2:15:12.03,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,保重\N{\fs38}Take care.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:18.13,2:15:21.18,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,虽然有说有笑 还时常说"再见"\N{\fs38}We laughed, we kept saying "see you soon",
Dialogue: 0,2:15:21.61,2:15:25.95,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但内心其实很清楚 我们不会再有机会相见了\N{\fs38}but inside, we both knew we'd never see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:26.21,2:15:30.72,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我们对此无能为力 这是注定会发生的\N{\fs38}And there was nothing we could do about it, it had to happen that way.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:30.90,2:15:33.32,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,正在发生\N{\fs38}And now it was happening.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:54.19,2:15:55.84,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,到底该怎么下船?\N{\fs38}How the hell we get off?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:01.82,2:16:04.52,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,再见 1900 保重\N{\fs38}Goodbye, Nineteen Hundred, take care.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:04.52,2:16:06.87,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,- 再见! - 别忘了我们\N{\fs38}- Bye! - Don't forget us.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:06.87,2:16:09.64,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,冬天记得穿羊毛背心\N{\fs38}Remember to wear your woollen vest in winter.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:09.64,2:16:11.80,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,保重 1900\N{\fs38}Take care Nineteen Hundred, take care.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:11.80,2:16:13.74,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,记得给我们写信\N{\fs38}Write us a letter sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:14.34,2:16:16.92,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,- 保重! - 记得向百老汇问好\N{\fs38}- Take care yourself! - Give my regards to Broadway.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:19.16,2:16:20.54,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,保重!\N{\fs38}Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,2:16:54.75,2:16:56.80,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他在干嘛 踩到狗屎了?\N{\fs38}What'd he do, step in shit?
Dialogue: 0,2:16:57.96,2:16:59.72,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,也许他忘了什么东西\N{\fs38}Maybe he just forgot something.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:59.78,2:17:01.93,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,也许是忘记了为什么要下船\N{\fs38}Maybe he's forgotten why he's getting off.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:14.44,2:18:16.44,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他在干嘛?\N{\fs38}What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,2:18:40.47,2:18:44.14,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他在舷梯上究竟看到了什么鬼东西\N{\fs38}Whatever he saw from that damned gangplank,
Dialogue: 0,2:18:44.55,2:18:48.87,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,又是什么样的思绪掠过他脑海\N{\fs38}what kind of thoughtscrossed his mind standing up there,
Dialogue: 0,2:18:48.98,2:18:50.98,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他从未和我说过\N{\fs38}he never told me.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:52.79,2:18:56.25,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,- 不 快走开! - 等下!\N{\fs38}- No, go away! - Wait!
Dialogue: 0,2:18:56.56,2:19:00.15,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我把钱都给你 拿去吧\N{\fs38}I'll give you all the money I have, take it.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:02.28,2:19:07.97,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那以后的很长时间里 他变得很奇怪 从不和别人说话\N{\fs38}He was strange for a long time after that. He wouldn't talk to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:08.36,2:19:12.99,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,总是喜欢一个人独处\N{\fs38}He preferred keeping to himself for days and days.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:13.20,2:19:16.84,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就好像被心结所困扰\N{\fs38}He seemed taken by very personal matters.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:17.02,2:19:20.57,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,然后有一天 当我坐在酒吧前台时...\N{\fs38}Then, one day, while I was sitting at the bar...
Dialogue: 0,2:19:20.77,2:19:21.97,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,瞧!\N{\fs38}Look!
Dialogue: 0,2:19:30.80,2:19:33.41,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,谢谢你送的那件大衣 马克斯 很合身\N{\fs38}Thanks for the coat, Max. Fit like a glove.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:34.73,2:19:36.96,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,很遗憾\N{\fs38}It was a real shame.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:38.44,2:19:42.44,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,不过现在我好多了 我不想下船了\N{\fs38}I'm much better now. I'm done with all that.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:52.65,2:19:55.45,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他不想是开玩笑的样子\N{\fs38}He looked like somebody who wasn't kidding,
Dialogue: 0,2:19:55.55,2:19:58.60,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,而是很清楚自己何去何从\N{\fs38}one who knew exactly where he was going.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:59.28,2:20:02.51,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就如同在坐在钢琴前弹奏一样\N{\fs38}Like when he'd sit at the pianoand start to play.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:03.29,2:20:05.96,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,从未有过任何的迟疑\N{\fs38}There were no doubts in his hands.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:06.06,2:20:10.44,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就好像琴键就在那等着他按下去\N{\fs38}It was as the keys had beenwaiting for those notes forever.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:10.74,2:20:13.85,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,似是随心所弹 信手捻来\N{\fs38}It seemed like he'd made them up then and there,
Dialogue: 0,2:20:13.95,2:20:20.10,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但其实这些音符早就在他的脑海里所形成\N{\fs38}yet somewhere in his head, those notes had been written all along.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:20.80,2:20:22.77,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那天 我就知道了\N{\fs38}Now, I know that on that day,
Dialogue: 0,2:20:22.77,2:20:27.36,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,1900就决定毕生守着钢琴\N{\fs38}Nineteen Hundred had decided to sit before the keyboard of his life
Dialogue: 0,2:20:27.42,2:20:30.59,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,演奏他最率性而为的音乐\N{\fs38}and start playing his most absurd music.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:31.07,2:20:35.67,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这些音乐就能代表他的余生\N{\fs38}And this music would have marked the rest of his days.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:31.62,2:21:36.04,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,看那个吹小号的 他不是疯子就是喝醉了\N{\fs38}Look at that guy with the trumpet, he's got be drunk or half crazy.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:36.04,2:21:39.04,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,瞧! 他边吹边哭起来了!\N{\fs38}Look! He's crying as he plays!
Dialogue: 0,2:22:03.54,2:22:08.46,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我在1933年8月21号那天 离开了维吉尼亚号\N{\fs38}I left the Virginian on August 21st, 1933,
Dialogue: 0,2:22:08.56,2:22:13.51,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,带着我的证件和薪水 以及一切其他的东西\N{\fs38}with my leave papers and back pay. Everything in order.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:13.51,2:22:16.63,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我知道早晚有一天我会对大海产生厌倦的\N{\fs38}I knew that sooner or later I'd have been through with the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:16.63,2:22:18.82,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,所以我选择离开\N{\fs38}So that's what I did.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:19.48,2:22:23.38,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那以后我再也没听到过1900或是维吉尼亚号的消息\N{\fs38}I heard no more about Nineteen Hundred or the Virginian.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:23.67,2:22:26.01,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但我从未忘记过他们\N{\fs38}Not that I ever forgot them.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:26.11,2:22:27.73,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他们也仍记得我\N{\fs38}On the contrary.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:28.28,2:22:30.64,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,在战争期间 我还时常会问自己...\N{\fs38}During the war, I'd always ask myself...
Dialogue: 0,2:22:31.26,2:22:35.12,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,如果1900在这儿 他会做什么?\N{\fs38}Who knows what Nineteen Hundred would do if he were here?
Dialogue: 0,2:22:35.15,2:22:37.31,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他会说些什么?\N{\fs38}Who knows what he'd say?
Dialogue: 0,2:22:37.50,2:22:39.79,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他绝对会说 "去他的战争"\N{\fs38}Fuck war, he'd say.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:39.98,2:22:44.69,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但从我嘴里说的 味道就变了\N{\fs38}But said by me, it wasn't the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:05.87,2:23:07.55,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,已经过了这么多年了\N{\fs38}A lot of time's gone by, you know.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:08.62,2:23:10.16,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,谁能保证他真的一直没下船?\N{\fs38}Who could say he really didn't leave?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:10.16,2:23:12.17,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,也许哪天天气好 他就跑到莫特大街\N{\fs38}Maybe one fine day, he went to Mott Street,
Dialogue: 0,2:23:12.17,2:23:13.77,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,到那间鱼店 去找那姑娘了\N{\fs38}the fish shop, to ask for the woman.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:15.11,2:23:17.00,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,也许吧\N{\fs38}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:25.65,2:27:30.16,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,嘿 小号手 你怎么了? 在船上站不稳了?\N{\fs38}Hey, Conn, what's the matter? You lose your sea legs?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:33.20,2:27:36.31,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你从哪儿找到的那个唱片?\N{\fs38}Where the hell did you find that record?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:44.18,2:27:47.05,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你这些年都在哪儿?\N{\fs38}What have you been up to all these years?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:53.28,2:27:55.20,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,创作音乐\N{\fs38}Making music.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:55.68,2:27:57.67,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,在战争期间也是?\N{\fs38}Even during the war?
Dialogue: 0,2:28:00.90,2:28:05.01,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,即使再也没有人跳舞\N{\fs38}Even when no one was dancing anymore.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:08.40,2:28:11.02,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,即使炮弹从身边飞过\N{\fs38}Even when the bombs were falling.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:14.45,2:28:17.80,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,音乐能为他们减轻痛苦\N{\fs38}The music helped them get better.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:19.19,2:28:21.09,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我指的是那些伤员\N{\fs38}The wounded, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:25.40,2:28:30.14,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,或是在他们渐渐死去的时候\N{\fs38}Or else it kept them entertained,
Dialogue: 0,2:28:30.67,2:28:34.65,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,至少是带着笑容离去\N{\fs38}as they slipped away into another world.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:36.84,2:28:41.26,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,有时如果有音乐陪伴的话\N{\fs38}Sometimes they didn't even mind the voyage
Dialogue: 0,2:28:41.77,2:28:44.61,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,他们就不怕那死亡之旅\N{\fs38}if they could listen to the music.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:47.14,2:28:50.47,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我每次都会陪他们走完终点\N{\fs38}Mine was the last face they saw.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:52.17,2:28:57.51,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我一直演奏 直到船到港\N{\fs38}And I kept playing till the ship got here.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:02.18,2:29:04.59,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这也算是一条船?\N{\fs38}Call this a ship?
Dialogue: 0,2:29:05.30,2:29:09.35,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,更像是装满火药的巨型炸弹\N{\fs38}It's more like a mountain of dynamite about to explode.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:10.08,2:29:12.74,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,有点危险 不是吗?\N{\fs38}A bit dangerous, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,2:29:18.84,2:29:20.63,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那你呢 马克斯?\N{\fs38}And you, Max?
Dialogue: 0,2:29:22.77,2:29:24.36,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你的小号呢?\N{\fs38}Where's your trumpet?
Dialogue: 0,2:29:26.89,2:29:29.96,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我前段时候已经放弃吹小号了\N{\fs38}I gave it up as well, a while back.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:30.38,2:29:34.51,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但你知道吗 我想重拾旧业\N{\fs38}But, you know, now I'm in the mood for starting again.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:35.44,2:29:38.49,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我脑子里有很多主意了\N{\fs38}I'm busting with new ideas.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:39.63,2:29:42.67,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我们搞个二重奏 你和我\N{\fs38}Let's start a duo, you and me.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:43.63,2:29:46.10,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,或者搞个乐队\N{\fs38}Or our own band:
Dialogue: 0,2:29:46.37,2:29:52.33,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,就叫"丹尼·博德曼·T·D·莱蒙·1900大乐队"!\N{\fs38}The "Danny Boodman T.D. lemonnineteen Hundred Big Band!"
Dialogue: 0,2:29:53.05,2:29:57.00,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,想着就让人兴奋! 我们会出名的\N{\fs38}It gets the blood going! We'd be a smash.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:00.26,2:30:03.57,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,来吧 1900 跟我一起下船\N{\fs38}Come on, Nineteen Hundred. Come with me. Let's get off.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:04.13,2:30:06.12,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我们在码头看这场焰火\N{\fs38}We'll watch the fireworks from the pier,
Dialogue: 0,2:30:06.12,2:30:09.17,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,然后再从头计划\N{\fs38}and then we'll start from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:10.78,2:30:13.58,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,有时候 就是得这样\N{\fs38}Sometimes that's the way you have to do it.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:13.58,2:30:16.63,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你会重新开始\N{\fs38}You go right back to the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:28.06,2:30:33.78,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,"只要你有个好故事 和听故事的人\N{\fs38}"You're never really done for as long as you've got a good story
Dialogue: 0,2:30:33.78,2:30:36.48,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这就不是你的末日"\N{\fs38}and someone to tell it to".
Dialogue: 0,2:30:37.14,2:30:38.92,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,记得吗?\N{\fs38}Remember?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:40.72,2:30:43.03,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,是你和我说的\N{\fs38}You told me that.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:45.65,2:30:49.61,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧你 你有这么多故事能说!\N{\fs38}Well, what a stack of stories you got now!
Dialogue: 0,2:30:50.50,2:30:53.37,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,整个世界都会为你疯狂\N{\fs38}The world would be hangingon your every word,
Dialogue: 0,2:30:54.61,2:30:58.16,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,为你的音乐疯狂\N{\fs38}and they'd go crazy for your music.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:00.74,2:31:02.12,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,相信我\N{\fs38}Believe me.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:07.84,2:31:10.30,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,整座城市...\N{\fs38}All that city...
Dialogue: 0,2:31:15.53,2:31:19.03,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你永远看不到尽头\N{\fs38}you just couldn't see an end to it.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:20.74,2:31:22.63,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,尽头!\N{\fs38}The end!
Dialogue: 0,2:31:23.49,2:31:28.54,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,尽头在哪儿? 指给我尽头在哪儿好吗?\N{\fs38}Please? You please just show me where it ends?
Dialogue: 0,2:31:31.93,2:31:35.04,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那天我在舷梯上感觉很好\N{\fs38}It was all very fineon that gangway
Dialogue: 0,2:31:35.47,2:31:39.56,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,还穿着你的那件大衣\N{\fs38}and I was grand, too, in my overcoat.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:40.24,2:31:42.82,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那天我看起来不错\N{\fs38}I cut quite a figure.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:43.51,2:31:48.70,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我决心下船 很坚定\N{\fs38}And I was getting off, guaranteed.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:49.63,2:31:52.46,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这个不是问题\N{\fs38}That's wasn't the problem.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:56.17,2:31:59.86,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,并不是我看见的东西让我停下的 马克斯\N{\fs38}It wasn't what I saw that stopped me, Max.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:00.97,2:32:03.56,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,是我所没看到的让我停下\N{\fs38}It was what I didn't see.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:04.35,2:32:06.37,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你能理解吗?\N{\fs38}Can you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,2:32:08.03,2:32:10.65,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我所看不到的\N{\fs38}What I didn't see.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:11.65,2:32:16.29,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,在那座漫无边际的城市 什么都有 但就是没有尽头\N{\fs38}In all that sprawling city, there was everything except an end.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:18.04,2:32:20.32,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,没有尽头\N{\fs38}There was no end.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:22.34,2:32:28.31,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我看不到事物的尽头\N{\fs38}What I did not see was where the whole thing came to an end,
Dialogue: 0,2:32:30.32,2:32:32.79,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,世界的尽头\N{\fs38}the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:39.92,2:32:42.12,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,比如说钢琴\N{\fs38}You take a piano.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:43.72,2:32:47.89,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,琴键有开始 也有结束\N{\fs38}Keys begin, the keys end.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:49.29,2:32:53.47,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你知道琴键有88个 没人会反对这点\N{\fs38}You know there are 88 of them, nobody can tell you any different.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:53.82,2:32:58.13,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,琴键是有限的 但你是无限的\N{\fs38}They are not infinite, you are infinite.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:59.78,2:33:05.01,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,在这些琴键上所创作的音乐 也是无限的\N{\fs38}And on those keys, the music that you can make is infinite.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:05.72,2:33:08.02,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这个我喜欢\N{\fs38}I like that.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:08.43,2:33:10.64,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我能接受\N{\fs38}That I can live by.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:10.95,2:33:12.58,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但是在舷梯上\N{\fs38}You get me up on that gangway
Dialogue: 0,2:33:12.58,2:33:13.89,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我仿佛看到了\N{\fs38}and you roll out in front of me
Dialogue: 0,2:33:13.89,2:33:17.90,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,成千上万个琴键 永无止境\N{\fs38}a keyboard of millions and billions of keys that never end.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:17.90,2:33:21.48,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这就是事实 马克斯 它们永远没有尽头\N{\fs38}And that's the truth, Max, that they never end.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:21.79,2:33:24.37,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那琴键是无限的\N{\fs38}That keyboard is infinite.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:25.27,2:33:30.40,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,而在这个无限大的键盘上 你根本就无法去演奏\N{\fs38}And if that keyboard is infinite,then on that keyboard there is no music you can play.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:31.23,2:33:33.88,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你坐在了错误的钢琴前\N{\fs38}You're sitting on the wrong bench.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:34.68,2:33:37.26,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这是上帝的钢琴\N{\fs38}That's God's piano.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:40.30,2:33:45.37,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,天啊 你没看见过那些街道吗? 光街道就有几千条\N{\fs38}Christ, did you see the streets? Just the streets. There were thousands of them.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:46.03,2:33:49.72,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你们是如何走的? 你怎么去选择走哪一条?\N{\fs38}How do you do it down there? How do you choose just one?
Dialogue: 0,2:33:50.96,2:33:55.56,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,一个女人 一栋房子\N{\fs38}One woman, one house,
Dialogue: 0,2:33:56.45,2:34:00.82,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,一块自己的地方 一片窗外的风景\N{\fs38}one piece of land to call your own, one landscape to look at,
Dialogue: 0,2:34:01.93,2:34:04.54,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,一种死亡的方式\N{\fs38}one way to die.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:07.92,2:34:10.63,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,所有的问题都要你去选择\N{\fs38}All that world just weighing down on you.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:10.63,2:34:12.66,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,然而这些都是永无止境 没有尽头\N{\fs38}You don't even know where it comes to an end.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:12.76,2:34:16.70,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你难道就从来没有被这种想法吓得要死吗?\N{\fs38}I mean, aren't you ever just scared of breaking apart at the thought of it?
Dialogue: 0,2:34:16.70,2:34:19.81,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这样永无止境日子是多么的恐怖\N{\fs38}At the enormity of living it?
Dialogue: 0,2:34:23.83,2:34:26.36,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我出生在这艘船上\N{\fs38}I was born on this ship.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:29.80,2:34:37.22,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我绕了世界好几圈 但每次只有两千人和我一起\N{\fs38}And the world passed me by, but two thousand people at a time.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:38.89,2:34:41.72,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这里有梦想\N{\fs38}And there were wishes here,
Dialogue: 0,2:34:43.14,2:34:46.81,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但不会超出船头和船尾\N{\fs38}but never more than fit between prow and stern.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:48.99,2:34:53.88,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你可以在有限的钢琴上表达出无限的快乐来\N{\fs38}You played out your happiness on a piano that was not infinite.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:54.69,2:34:57.78,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这样才是我的生活\N{\fs38}I learned to live that way.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:01.31,2:35:03.10,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,陆地?\N{\fs38}Land?
Dialogue: 0,2:35:05.29,2:35:08.81,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,陆地对我来说是艘过大的船\N{\fs38}Land is a ship too big for me.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:10.99,2:35:14.07,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,太漂亮的女人\N{\fs38}It's a woman too beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:15.94,2:35:20.78,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,过长的旅途 太浓的香水\N{\fs38}It's a voyage too long. Perfume too strong.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:21.96,2:35:25.53,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这支曲子我不知道从何弹起\N{\fs38}It's music I don't know how to make.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:29.05,2:35:32.12,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我永远离不开这条船\N{\fs38}I could never get off this ship.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:35.07,2:35:39.69,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但我可以结束自己的生命\N{\fs38}At best, I can step off my life.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:41.97,2:35:46.48,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,反正对别人来说 我从未出生过\N{\fs38}After all, I don't exist for anyone.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:50.70,2:35:53.54,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,除了你 马克斯\N{\fs38}You're the exception, Max.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:55.27,2:35:58.52,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,只有你知道我在这儿\N{\fs38}You're the only one who knows that I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:00.61,2:36:03.07,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你是个少数派\N{\fs38}You're a minority.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:03.78,2:36:06.68,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你最好习惯这一点\N{\fs38}And you'd better get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:11.01,2:36:13.32,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,原谅我吧 朋友\N{\fs38}Forgive me, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:14.97,2:36:17.55,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我不下船了\N{\fs38}But I'm not getting off.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:47.62,2:37:49.20,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,嘿 马克斯\N{\fs38}Hey, Max.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:51.56,2:37:54.11,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,想象一下我到了天国之门的样子\N{\fs38}Picture the scene at the Golden Gates.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:54.52,2:37:58.42,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,有人会去搜寻我叫什么 然后发现没这个人\N{\fs38}Some guy searching a list trying to find my name, not finding it.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:59.42,2:38:01.65,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你叫什么来着?\N{\fs38}What did you say your name was again?
Dialogue: 0,2:38:01.75,2:38:03.42,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我叫1900\N{\fs38}Nineteen Hundred.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:04.62,2:38:09.86,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,尼曼 奈丁格 奈斯多克... 尼特汀?\N{\fs38}Niemann, Nightingale, Ninestock... Nittledeen?
Dialogue: 0,2:38:09.96,2:38:12.79,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,先生 我是在船上出生的\N{\fs38}Well, you see, sir. I was born on a ship.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:13.61,2:38:14.71,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你说什么?\N{\fs38}Beg your pardon?
Dialogue: 0,2:38:14.72,2:38:19.12,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我在船上出生 长大 死亡的 也许我没在任何名单上\N{\fs38}Born, raised, and died on a ship. Maybe I'm not registered there.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:19.22,2:38:22.73,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,嗯 船沉了?\N{\fs38}Yeah, Shipwreck?
Dialogue: 0,2:38:22.83,2:38:25.77,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,不 是六吨半的炸药炸掉的\N{\fs38}No, six and a half tons of dynamite.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:28.39,2:38:30.16,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,感觉好点了吗?\N{\fs38}Feeling better now?
Dialogue: 0,2:38:30.26,2:38:34.62,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,嗯 好多了 只是丢了个手臂\N{\fs38}Yeah, I'm fine, except I lost an arm.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:34.92,2:38:36.46,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,手臂?\N{\fs38}An arm?
Dialogue: 0,2:38:36.56,2:38:38.97,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,嗯 爆炸时候断掉了\N{\fs38}Yes, in the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:40.84,2:38:43.07,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,嗯 那边有几个断臂\N{\fs38}Well, you should be able to find one over there.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:44.28,2:38:46.60,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你的哪条手臂断掉了?\N{\fs38}Which one did you say you were missing?
Dialogue: 0,2:38:46.70,2:38:48.44,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,左边的\N{\fs38}Left, sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:48.95,2:38:52.84,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我非常非常地抱歉\N{\fs38}I'm dreadfully sorry.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:53.72,2:38:57.51,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,这儿只有两条右胳膊\N{\fs38}We only seem to have two rights.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:57.61,2:38:58.88,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,两条右臂?\N{\fs38}Two right arms?
Dialogue: 0,2:38:58.88,2:39:00.70,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs38}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:00.80,2:39:02.61,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,恐怕就是如此\N{\fs38}Afraid so.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:02.71,2:39:07.00,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你觉得这样合适吗...\N{\fs38}Would you mind awfully if....
Dialogue: 0,2:39:08.18,2:39:09.62,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,什么?\N{\fs38}If I what?
Dialogue: 0,2:39:09.72,2:39:13.78,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,您觉得把右臂安在左边合适吗?\N{\fs38}Well, if you take a right arm instead of a left?
Dialogue: 0,2:39:17.28,2:39:22.82,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,嗯 有总比没有好吧\N{\fs38}Well, all things considered, a right arm than nothing, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:22.92,2:39:25.24,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我也觉得如此\N{\fs38}Couldn't agree more.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:25.59,2:39:30.86,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,还有 这两条手臂一个是黑人的 一个人白人的\N{\fs38}By the way, we have one black armand one white arm.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:30.90,2:39:33.82,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,哦 不... 我要一样的颜色 谢谢\N{\fs38}Oh, no.... Matching color, please.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:33.82,2:39:39.60,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我绝对没有种族歧视 只是想让两边颜色对称\N{\fs38}I have nothing against the other race, but it's just a question of aesthetics.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:43.08,2:39:45.50,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,你别取笑我哦 马克斯\N{\fs38}No laughing matter, Max.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:47.03,2:39:52.89,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我够惨的了 要用两只右手渡过永生\N{\fs38}What a cock-up, spend eternity with two right arms?
Dialogue: 0,2:39:53.30,2:39:56.42,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,怎样在胸前划十字啊?\N{\fs38}I mean, how would you make the sign of the cross?
Dialogue: 0,2:40:11.38,2:40:13.33,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,嘿 马克斯\N{\fs38}Hey, Max.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:14.99,2:40:18.21,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,想象一下 我用两只右手能弹出什么曲子\N{\fs38}Imagine the music I could play with two right arms.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:19.44,2:40:22.28,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,希望天堂有钢琴弹\N{\fs38}Hope I can find a piano up there.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:29.60,2:40:32.17,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,好 就这样\N{\fs38}Okay, that's fine like that.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:40.04,2:40:44.61,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,- 慢慢地 - 抓住那里\N{\fs38}- Slowly. - Get hold of it there.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:18.30,2:42:20.79,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,如果换是你 你会怎么做?\N{\fs38}What would you have done in my shoes?
Dialogue: 0,2:42:22.88,2:42:24.89,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs38}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:27.58,2:42:30.83,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,也许我会感觉自己很没用\N{\fs38}I wouldn't probably have felt quite useless.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:38.33,2:42:43.86,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,所有的故事到此就结束了 没有其他要说的了\N{\fs38}Sooner or later all stories end, and there's nothing left to add.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:49.14,2:42:52.08,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,无论如何 谢谢你 老爷子\N{\fs38}Anyhow, thanks, pops.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:13.14,2:43:18.60,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,小号手 有件事我还不明白\N{\fs38}Conn, there's just one thing I don't get.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:19.67,2:43:23.42,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,是谁把那些残破的唱片藏到钢琴里的?\N{\fs38}Who hide the broken record inside the piano?
Dialogue: 0,2:43:26.56,2:43:28.30,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,近在眼前\N{\fs38}You're looking at him.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:29.93,2:43:33.93,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,那你并不是一无是处的\N{\fs38}So you weren't so useless after all.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:42.65,2:43:44.23,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,小号手\N{\fs38}Conn.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:48.24,2:43:49.87,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,拿着\N{\fs38}Here.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:53.41,2:43:58.16,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,拿着你的小号 你会需要它的\N{\fs38}Take your trumpet. Well, you'll be needing it.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:00.42,2:44:01.53,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,但我...\N{\fs38}But I....
Dialogue: 0,2:44:01.68,2:44:03.43,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,不必担心那些钱了\N{\fs38}Never mind the money.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:04.10,2:44:07.50,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,好的故事比旧小号值钱得多\N{\fs38}A good story's worth more than an old trumpet.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:15.15,2:44:17.16,Default-微软雅黑 中英双字,,0,0,0,,好吧 老爷子\N{\fs38}Okay, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:13.28,2:45:25.12,Default-微软雅黑 粗,,0,0,0,,海上钢琴师 片终
Dialogue: 0,2:45:26.53,2:45:29.70,Default-微软雅黑 粗,,0,0,0,,导演 吉赛贝·托纳多雷


